,'<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nWrappli is Australia\'s premier provider of on-car outdoor advertising. Aussie drivers can earn some extra income while going about their daily commutes. Drivers get their cars wrapped in advertising campaigns and earn money while they drive around; whether going to work, shopping centre, or even a mates house.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with WRAPPLI:\r\n\r\nHold an Australian Full Drivers license\r\nHave a clean driving and criminal record\r\nCurrently own or lease a 2008 or newer vehicle in clean and damage-free condition.\r\nComply with all Wrappli terms and conditions.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.wrappli.com.au/drivers/\">http://www.wrappli.com.au/drivers/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.wrappli.com.au/faq/\">http://www.wrappli.com.au/faq/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease request terms and conditions from Wrappli directly. If you have any questions please email: info@wrappli.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become a part of the Wrappli community:\r\n\r\nDownload the Wrappli app, available on the Apple App/ Android Store\r\nRegister your details.\r\nAfter logging in your first 100kms, they will match your daily commute habits to campaigns they have on board.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.wrappli.com.au/drivers/#download\">http://www.wrappli.com.au/drivers/#download</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the WRAPPLI website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nThis will depend on the driving conditions you will need to meet, as a guide, people earn $300-$400 per month on average.','no'),(1366,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_0_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1367,'options_compatibility_check_providers_0_exclusion','','no'),(1368,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_0_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1369,'options_compatibility_check_providers_0_country','AU','no'),(1370,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_0_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1371,'options_compatibility_check_providers','70','no'),(1372,'_options_compatibility_check_providers','field_5ba360ff8b5f6','no'),(1378,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_logo','309','no'),(1379,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1380,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_name','Zoom2u','no'),(1381,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1382,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_Website','www.zoom2u.com.au','no'),(1383,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1384,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_potential','$100 to $2000 a week','no'),(1385,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1386,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nZoom2u is a courier marketplace designed to connect you with customers looking to have their parcel delivered throughout Australia. Today, Zoom2u has customers in Sydney, Melbourne, Canberra, Brisbane, Adelaide, Perth, and Gold Coast, and they are expanding network of coverage across Australia. Joining is free and you have complete flexibility regarding when you work.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Zoom2u:\r\n\r\nA valid Australian drivers license\r\nThe right to work in Australia (Citizenship, permanent residency, or a working VISA)\r\nAn ABN (Australian Business Number)\r\nA reliable vehicle with comprehensive insurance coverage\r\nA smartphone with a reliable internet connection\r\nYou will also require a clean police record with the Australian Federal Police, as we require mandatory police checks.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zoom2u.com.au/become-a-driver/\">https://www.zoom2u.com.au/become-a-driver/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zoom2u.com.au/driver-faqs/\">https://www.zoom2u.com.au/driver-faqs/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://courier.zoom2u.com/#/register\">https://courier.zoom2u.com/#/register</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zoom2u.com.au/customer-terms/\">https://www.zoom2u.com.au/customer-terms/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zoom2u.com.au/privacy/\">https://www.zoom2u.com.au/privacy/</a>\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please call Zoom2u on 1300 326 150 or follow this link:<a href=\"https://www.zoom2u.com.au/contact-us/\"> https://www.zoom2u.com.au/contact-us/</a>\r\n<h4><strong></strong><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Zoom2u:\r\n\r\nTo become a Zoom2u driver and gain access to the marketplace platform, you have to provide answers to 11 questions. To start, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://courier.zoom2u.com/#/register\">https://courier.zoom2u.com/#/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Zoom2u website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nThis will depend on your availability and the jobs you get, as a guide, people can earn anything from $100 to $2000 a week on average.','no'),(1387,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1388,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_exclusion','','no'),(1389,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1390,'options_compatibility_check_providers_1_country','AU','no'),(1391,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_1_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1392,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_logo','312','no'),(1393,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1394,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_name','Car Next Door','no'),(1395,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1396,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_Website','www.carnextdoor.com.au','no'),(1397,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1398,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_potential',' $2000 in your first year','no'),(1399,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1400,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nCar Next Door is a company that facilitates peer-to-peer car rental, a system by which individuals may rent privately owned vehicles on an hourly or daily basis to other registered users of the service platform of Car Next Door. If you dont use your car every day, Car Next Door is an easy, reliable way to offset the costs of owning your car by renting out to a community of insured, trusted borrowers while you arent using it.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Car Next Door:\r\n\r\nTo lend your car:\r\nYou can rent your car out while your license is suspended or even if you don\'t have a license or you are on holiday.\r\nYour $60/month Owner Membership includes comprehensive insurance for damage and theft and third party loss. You no longer need your own comprehensive insurance. For more information follow the instruction on List your car application.\r\n\r\nTo borrow a car:\r\nYou must be at least 18 years old and no more than 75 years old;\r\nNot have had any license suspensions or disqualifications, major traffic violations, or alcohol/drug related driving incidents in the past 5 years;\r\nNot have been convicted of, or have any pending convictions for, a criminal offence in any jurisdiction;\r\nHold a full unrestricted license and have been licensed for at least two years.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all terms and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car\">https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car#rates\">https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car#rates</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb\">https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb/articles/204824399-Am-I-eligible-to-join-Car-Next-Door-\">https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb/articles/204824399-Am-I-eligible-to-join-Car-Next-Door-</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/terms-of-use\">https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/terms-of-use</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb/categories/200551519-Renting-your-car-out#insurance-trust-and-safety\">https://support.carnextdoor.com.au/hc/en-gb/categories/200551519-Renting-your-car-out#insurance-trust-and-safety</a>\r\n\r\nFor more urgent information, use live chat or for non-urgent enquiries or feedback, please email info@carnextdoor.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Car Next Door:\r\n\r\nYou need to create your profile on the Car Next Door website, please follow the links below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/list-your-car\">https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/list-your-car</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Car Next Door website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nIf youre in one of their target postcodes in Sydney, Melbourne or Brisbane, they guarantee that your car earns $2000 in its first year.\r\n\r\nYour share of time-based income each month 50% up to $240, 75% after that.\r\n\r\nFor all details visit:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car#rates\">https://www.carnextdoor.com.au/how-to-list-your-car#rates</a>','no'),(1401,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1402,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_exclusion','','no'),(1403,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1404,'options_compatibility_check_providers_2_country','AU','no'),(1405,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_2_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1414,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_logo','314','no'),(1415,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1416,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_name','Drive My Car','no'),(1417,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1418,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_Website','www.drivemycar.com.au','no'),(1419,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1420,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_potential','$50 to $800 a month','no'),(1421,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1422,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nDriveMyCar is Australia\'s first and largest peer-to-peer car rental service. They make it possible for people to rent cars from other people with confidence. They do this by creating a \"trusted marketplace\" where Owners list their vehicles for FREE and Renters find and book the vehicles after passing their verification processes. Coverage is provided for accidental damage and theft. DriveMyCar is specialized in rental periods from 2 days - 365 days. For Owners, they offer the ability to earn money from a vehicle they are not using. DriveMyCar is owned by Collaborate Corporation Limited an ASX listed company.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with DriveMyCar:\r\n\r\nTo lend your car, your car is:\r\nLess than 10 years old\r\nLess than 150,000 kilometres\r\nUnder $75,000 in value\r\nWell maintained with up to date servicing\r\nRegistered with appropriate CTP insurance\r\nVehicle must be available for rental periods of at least 7 consecutive days.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/howitworks\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/howitworks</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Rent-Out-Your-Car\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Rent-Out-Your-Car</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/faq\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Trust\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Trust</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Insurance-Information\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Insurance-Information</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/terms-and-conditions\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/terms-and-conditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/documents/OWNER_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS.pdf\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/documents/OWNER_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS.pdf</a>\r\n\r\nFor any further informations please use live chat on the website or for all general enquiries, please call DriveMyCar on 1300 980 706.\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with DriveMyCar:\r\n\r\nYou need to create your profile and list your car here:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Account/AddListing\">https://www.drivemycar.com.au/Account/AddListing</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the DriveMyCar website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nEarning will depend on your listing and car availability. on average, you can earn anything from $50 to $800 a month.','no'),(1423,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1424,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_exclusion','','no'),(1425,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1426,'options_compatibility_check_providers_3_country','AU','no'),(1427,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_3_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1428,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_logo','318','no'),(1429,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1430,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_name','Go Catch','no'),(1431,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1432,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_Website','www.gocatch.com','no'),(1433,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1434,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_potential','from $6.80 minimum fare','no'),(1435,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1436,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nGoCatch is a taxi booking app. From its inception in 2011, its core purpose has been to use innovation and technology to transform the taxi industry and dramatically improve the passenger and driver experience. GoCatch recognised how frustrated Australians were with the service and reliability of the taxi industry. There are multiple options to sign up as a GoCatch driver.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with GoCatch:\r\n\r\nBe at least 21 years of age\r\nHold a full, unrestricted Australian Drivers License for a minimum period of 12 months\r\nHave a current Driver Authority / Accreditation / Extension in your home state (see below)\r\nHave an iOS or Android phone\r\nBe able to speak fluent English\r\nYoull also be required to have the correct license and necessary documentation.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gocatch.com/driver/economy/\">https://www.gocatch.com/driver/economy/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/205697229-GoCatch-Code-of-Conduct\">https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/205697229-GoCatch-Code-of-Conduct</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gocatch.com/privacy-policy/\">https://www.gocatch.com/privacy-policy/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gocatch.com/legal/\">https://www.gocatch.com/legal/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/categories/200266549-Driver-Support\">https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/categories/200266549-Driver-Support</a>\r\n\r\nFor any further informations, please use this link below to contact GoCach:\r\n<a href=\"https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\">https://gocatch.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/requests/new<strong></strong></a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become a GoCatch driver, you have to take 3 steps, as follow:\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Sign Up Online\r\nFirstly, click the sign-up button to create your driver profile. Then, upload the required documentation.\r\nStep 2 - Download The Driver App\r\nAfter sign up, youll need to download the GoCatch Driver app from the App Store or Google Play.\r\nStep 3 - Await Approval\r\n\r\nSign up available through the link below.\r\n<a href=\"https://portal.gocatch.com/driver-login#/sign-up\">https://portal.gocatch.com/driver-login#/sign-up</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the GoCatch website before starting.\r\n\r\n<strong>How much you can earn</strong>\r\n\r\nEarning will depend on your availability and schedules, the minimum economy fare is $6.80. Driver earns 85% of the fare.\r\nFor all details, please visit GoCatch website:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gocatch.com/driver/resources/fares/\">https://www.gocatch.com/driver/resources/fares/</a>','no'),(1437,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1438,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_exclusion','','no'),(1439,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1440,'options_compatibility_check_providers_4_country','AU','no'),(1441,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_4_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1442,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_logo','321','no'),(1443,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1444,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_name','Uber','no'),(1445,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1446,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_Website','www.uber.com','no'),(1447,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1448,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_potential',' $15 to $25 an hour','no'),(1449,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1450,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nUBER is a technology platform; smartphone apps connect drivers and riders. When a nearby driver accepts your request, your app displays an estimated time of arrival for the driver heading to your pickup location. Your app notifies you when the driver is about to arrive. In Australia, it is flexible to become an UBER driver partner. You can drive with UBER any time, day or night, 365 days a year. When and where you drive is always up to you. You can become an UBER driver and drive people, or you can sign up with UBER Eats, Business, Freight, or Health. different terms and conditions apply.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with UBER:\r\n\r\nBe at least 21 years of age\r\nHave access to a vehicle that meets UBER\'s vehicle requirements (your own or rented)\r\nHold a valid full drivers license in your state or territory\r\nHave held a full drivers license in any Australian state or territory for at least 12 months (exceptions apply in certain states and territories)\r\nProvide all the necessary documents required in your state or territory\r\nBe listed as an insured driver for the vehicle you plan to drive.\r\nThere is also a list of documents and background cheek you need to meet.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/requirements/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/requirements/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/safety/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/safety/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/insurance/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/insurance/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/Sydney/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/Sydney/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/delivery/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/delivery/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/vehicle-solutions/\">https://www.uber.com/en-AU/drive/vehicle-solutions/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, pls contact UBER on 1300 091 272.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become an UBER driver partner, you have to follow 3 simple steps, as follow:\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Sign up online on the website or App\r\nStep 2 - Upload requested documents\r\nStep 3 - Get a vehicle inspection\r\n\r\nYou can sign up for UBER people driving on the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/a/join?exp=70801c\">https://www.uber.com/a/join?exp=70801c</a>\r\nor\r\nYou can sign up to deliver for UBER on the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.uber.com/a/signup/drive/deliver\">https://www.uber.com/a/signup/drive/deliver</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the UBER website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nUBER has different rates for different peak and off-peak times. UBER takes 25% commission off your fare. In Australia, drivers earn $15 to $25 an hour on average.\r\n\r\nPlease contact UBER for the most up to date rates, as this is regularly being updated.','no'),(1451,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1452,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_exclusion','','no'),(1453,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1454,'options_compatibility_check_providers_5_country','AU','no'),(1455,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_5_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1456,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_logo','322','no'),(1457,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1458,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_name','shebah','no'),(1459,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1460,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_Website','https://shebah.com.au','no'),(1461,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1462,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_potential',' $15 to $25 an hour','no'),(1463,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1464,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_description','<h4>How it works</h4>\r\nSHEBAH is Australias first and only active all-female rideshare service getting women and children where they need to go.\r\nThey exist so that women in Australia can live their lives to the fullest and feel limitless. SHEBAH is a company for women; driven by women. Our SHEBAH woman drivers mean working when it suits you, feeling safe about who you pick u,p and experiencing financial freedomas SHEBAH drivers keep 85% of their fares.\r\n<h4>Minimum Requirements</h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with SHEBAH:\r\n\r\nYoure at least 21 years old.\r\nYou have an iOS or Android phone.\r\nYou can comfortably and confidently speak English.\r\nYou agree to follow our vulnerable passenger guidelines.\r\nYouve held an unrestricted Australian drivers license for at least 12 months.\r\nYou have access to a car in excellent condition, with a minimum of four doors.\r\nYou have an ABN and are registered for GST.\r\nPlease note that there are additional requirements per each state.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://shebah.com.au/faqs/\">https://shebah.com.au/faqs/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://shebah.com.au/drive/\">https://shebah.com.au/drive/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://driver.shebah.com.au/register/step1a\">https://driver.shebah.com.au/register/step1a</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://shebah.com.au/privacy-policy/\">https://shebah.com.au/privacy-policy/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://shebah.com.au/terms-conditions-2/\">https://shebah.com.au/terms-conditions-2/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, pls contact SHEBAH on 03 8640 9954 or follow the link to leave a message.\r\n<h4>How to start</h4>\r\nTo become a SHEBAH driver, you have to follow 5 simple steps on the link below:\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Read terms and conditions\r\nStep 2 - Basic personal information, including ABN\r\nStep 3 - Upload documents\r\nStep 4 - Provide vehicle information\r\nStep 5 - Provide bank details information\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://driver.shebah.com.au/register/step1\">https://driver.shebah.com.au/register/step1</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the SHEBAH website before starting.\r\n<h4>How much you can earn</h4>\r\nYou will keep 85% of your fares, and your fares are inclusive of GST. SHEBAH have different rates for different peak and off-peak times.\r\nLatest information on SHEBAH earnings are:\r\nTime zones are broken down into 3 colours.\r\nGreen is 4am - 5pm. The booking fee is $3.00 and it\'s $0.40 per minute and $1.10 per km\r\nOrange is 5pm - 12pm, $5 booking fee $1.00 per minute $3.00 per km\r\nRed is 12pm - 4am, $6.00 booking fee $1.20 per minute and $4.00 per km.\r\n\r\nPlease contact SHEBAH for the most up to date rates as this is regularly being updated.','no'),(1465,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1466,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_exclusion','a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"male\";}','no'),(1467,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1468,'options_compatibility_check_providers_6_country','AU','no'),(1469,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_6_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1470,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_logo','325','no'),(1471,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1472,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_name','Menulog','no'),(1473,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1474,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_Website','www.menulog.com.au','no'),(1475,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1476,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_potential','$15-$20 per hour ','no'),(1477,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1478,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nMenulog is Australias largest online food ordering platform, offering you the widest variety of delicious foods to discover and have delivered straight to your door. As an independent contractor making deliveries via the Menulog platform, you are paid for delivering food from their partner restaurants to their customers.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Menulog:\r\n\r\nYoure at least 18 years old\r\nDriving license\r\nPassport/Right to Work\r\nCertificate showing your vehicle is insured/registered\r\nAustralian Business Number (ABN)\r\nYou will also have some legal terms youll have to review and agree to.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.menulog.com.au/privacy-policy\">https://www.menulog.com.au/privacy-policy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://couriers.menulog.com.au/application\">https://couriers.menulog.com.au/application</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.menulog.com.au/menulog_privacy\">https://www.menulog.com.au/menulog_privacy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.menulog.com.au/menulog_terms_of_use\">https://www.menulog.com.au/menulog_terms_of_use</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, pls contact Menulog via the link below: <a href=\"https://www.menulog.com.au/contact_us\">https://www.menulog.com.au/contact_us</a><strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become a Menulog driver, you have to follow 3 simple steps:\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Create an account (see link below) upload your documents, and complete a quick screening call with a member of our team.\r\nStep 2- Download the Courier App. Set your availability within the Courier App and pick up any available open runs\r\nStep 3 - Earn Money. Once you have all the tools you need, you can start making deliveries to earn extra money.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://couriers.menulog.com.au/application\">https://couriers.menulog.com.au/application</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Menulog website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nAs an independent Menulog courier, you earn money through your delivery fee which is based off distance and driving time, so it will vary by order. You can expect around $15-$20 per hour on average.','no'),(1479,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1480,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_exclusion','','no'),(1481,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1482,'options_compatibility_check_providers_7_country','AU','no'),(1483,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_7_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1484,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_logo','328','no'),(1485,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1486,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_name','Go People','no'),(1487,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1488,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_Website','www.gopeople.com.au','no'),(1489,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1490,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_potential','$25 per hour','no'),(1491,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1492,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nGo People is changing the delivery industry by disrupting legacy delivery and courier industry rules, simplifying the point-to-point delivery process for both consumers and businesses, fulfilling the gap in service demand, raising service standards, and facilitating transparent and competitive pricing. Customers (Senders) book their deliveries and pay via the Web-based portal or smartphone app. A Runner (driver/delivery person) can then apply for a job via the smartphone app, with the most suitable Runner chosen. Then the selected Runner collects the parcel(s) from the pick-up location and delivers it to the recipient.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Go People:\r\n\r\nBe over 18 years old\r\nOwn a smartphone\r\nHave a car or a van\r\nHave an ABN\r\nYoure at least 18 years old\r\nThere will be a quick quiz, so make sure you read the Runner Knowledge Base and answer every question. You need 90% to pass!\r\nThere will be also a 30min call\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gopeople.com.au/runner/\">https://www.gopeople.com.au/runner/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gopeople.com.au/knowledgebase/runner/\">https://www.gopeople.com.au/knowledgebase/runner/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gopeople.com.au/on-demand-jobs/\">https://www.gopeople.com.au/on-demand-jobs/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gopeople.com.au/terms-shift-runner/\">https://www.gopeople.com.au/terms-shift-runner/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gopeople.com.au/privacy/\">https://www.gopeople.com.au/privacy/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Go People on 1300 416 722 or email: support@gopeople.com.au<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become a Go People driver (runner) you have to follow 6 simple steps:\r\n\r\nDownload Go People app, and then:\r\n1. Fill in basic personal details\r\n2. Enter your ABN\r\n3. Take a selfie of you and your license\r\n4. Describe your car, attach a photo\r\n5. Pass the online Runner quiz\r\n6. Complete a training call.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Go People website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou could start earning $25 per hour right away with Go People but if you have your own van, delivery runners can earn up to $32 per hour for GoSHIFT work.','no'),(1493,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1494,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_exclusion','','no'),(1495,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1496,'options_compatibility_check_providers_8_country','AU','no'),(1497,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_8_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1498,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_logo','330','no'),(1499,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1500,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_name','Sherpa','no'),(1501,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1502,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_Website','www.sherpa.net.au','no'),(1503,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1504,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_potential','$15 per hour in average','no'),(1505,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1506,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nSherpa is a delivery technology company that is transforming the way local goods move around the city. Sherpa platform enables anyone to get (almost) any product delivered within a matter of hours. Joining the Sherpa tribe is not just about moving parcels from A to B, its about being a part of something bigger and changing the way the world moves things. Whether its flowers, parcels, cakes, or alcohol, they like to think they deliver moments of happiness.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Sherpa:\r\n\r\nA vehicle with a minimum of Compulsory Third Party insurance\r\nAn active ABN\r\nA valid drivers license (International and foreign licenses accepted)\r\nA smartphone (iPhone or Android 4.0)\r\nA good level of English\r\nAn upbeat and positive attitude\r\nGreat communication and presentation skills\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.sherpa.net.au/hc/end-us/categories/115000294792-Sherpa-Drivers\">https://help.sherpa.net.au/hc/end-us/categories/115000294792-Sherpa-Drivers</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sherpa.net.au/terms\">https://www.sherpa.net.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sherpa.net.au/privacy-policy\">https://www.sherpa.net.au/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Sherpa on 1300 13 77 18\r\nor email on: info@sherpa.net.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo become a Sherpa driver, you have to follow the 5 steps:\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Register with your first name / last name / email address / mobile number / type of vehicle / home address / password. (link below to start)\r\nOnce you click register, you\'ll receive a confirmation link in your inbox which prompts you to login to your account.\r\nStep 2 - Once logged to your account, fill out profile picture / valid photo ID / Bank details or PayPal Account (so we can pay you) and your ABN.\r\nStep 3 - Read the Contractor Agreement + the Onboarding Manual and tick the boxes (under My Account / Profile)\r\nStep 4 - Pass online quiz about the Onboarding Manual (must achieve 90% to move to the last step)\r\nStep 4 - Book a 2-min call so they can check your English.\r\nStep 5 - Once your profile has been approved, you\'ll be able to download the Sherpa Driver app and start accepting deliveries.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://deliveries.sherpa.net.au/couriers/signup\">https://deliveries.sherpa.net.au/couriers/signup</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Sherpa website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nSherpas drivers are paid per delivery.\r\nEach job has its own specific price which is determined by:\r\nThe distance between pickup and delivery locations\r\nTimeframe to complete the delivery (2hr, 4hr, Same Day)\r\nItem quantity\r\nVehicle requested\r\nThe average delivery price is roughly $15 but prices range from $8 to $50+.\r\n\r\nPlease note that all job prices are GST inclusive.','no'),(1507,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1508,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_exclusion','','no'),(1509,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1510,'options_compatibility_check_providers_9_country','AU','no'),(1511,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_9_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1516,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_0_average_value','','no'),(1517,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_0_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1518,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_1_average_value','1000','no'),(1519,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_1_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1520,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_2_average_value','1000','no'),(1521,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_2_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1522,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_3_average_value','350','no'),(1523,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_3_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1524,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_4_average_value','1000','no'),(1525,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_4_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1526,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_5_average_value','200','no'),(1527,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_5_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1528,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_6_average_value','1000','no'),(1529,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_6_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1530,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_7_average_value','1000','no'),(1531,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_7_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1532,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_8_average_value','100','no'),(1533,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_8_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1534,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_9_average_value','500','no'),(1535,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_9_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1536,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_10_average_value','500','no'),(1537,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_10_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1538,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_11_average_value','500','no'),(1539,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_11_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1540,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_12_average_value','300','no'),(1541,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_12_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1542,'options_compatibility_check_0_questions_13_average_value','250','no'),(1543,'_options_compatibility_check_0_questions_13_average_value','field_5ba3789d310bc','no'),(1546,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_logo','333','no'),(1547,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1548,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_name','Hop','no'),(1549,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1550,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_Website','www.myhop.io','no'),(1551,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1552,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_potential','from $15 to $35 an hour','no'),(1553,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1554,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nThere is always a solution for those who dont own a car, HOP and Hertz have partnered to provide a deal for HOP drivers to use their cars and earn money on demand. Choose your rental period and start driving and earning. To make things better, insurance and maintenance are always included. They also offer included kilometres and cover the cost of petrol for on-demand rentals. You can rent for an hour or up to three months. HOP offers complete flexibility so you can choose when you drive.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with HOP:\r\n\r\nYou must be at least 25 years\r\nOwn an iPhone\r\nTheyll carry out background checks and license record reviews\r\nMore information for you will be further outlined in an email following registration.\r\nNSW drivers are required to hold an Authority to Drive if they dont hold one already or are not registered Taxi or Hire Car drivers.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.myhop.io/terms.html\">http://www.myhop.io/terms.html</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.myhop.io/privacy.html\">http://www.myhop.io/privacy.html</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact HOP.\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with HOP, you follow the application on their website on the link below.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.myhop.io/\">http://www.myhop.io/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease follow the instructions you get via email from HOP.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the HOP website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nRiders pay you through the HOP app or the Square Chip &amp; Pin reader. Drivers receive the full fare (excluding any card surcharges or booking fees) through their nominated bank account. Funds are deposited in the drivers account on a 2 to 3 days cycle from the time a transaction is processed. On average, you can earn from $15 to $35 an hour.','no'),(1555,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1556,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_exclusion','','no'),(1557,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1558,'options_compatibility_check_providers_10_country','AU','no'),(1559,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_10_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1560,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_logo','338','no'),(1561,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1562,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_name','Splend','no'),(1563,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1564,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_Website','www.splend.com.au','no'),(1565,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1566,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_potential','$1000 per week (45h)','no'),(1567,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1568,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nThere is always a solution for those who dont own a car, more and more people are choosing to rent a car to drive with rideshare on-demand applications such as Uber and others. Splend rents cars on flexible agreements. After a minimum period of four or six weeks, depending on the plan you choose, you can provide your two-week termination notice and hand back the car. Thats all there is to it! There are no exit fees to worry about, so all the choice and flexibility is yours. When renting a car from Splend, you do not need finance as you are paying a simple weekly rental fee. Splend rents vehicles to drivers in Sydney, Melbourne, Perth, Brisbane, Adelaide, Canberra, Gold Coast, and Newcastle.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Splend:\r\n\r\nYou must be at least 25 years old\r\nLive within 30km of your capital city CBD\r\nOwn a smartphone\r\nHave a current valid Australian Drivers License\r\nHave no criminal record\r\nHave a good driving record\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.splend.com.au/help/#rent\">https://www.splend.com.au/help/#rent</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.splend.com.au/plans-pricing/rent\">https://www.splend.com.au/plans-pricing/rent</a>\r\nRequest terms and conditions from Splend team.\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Splend on 1800 775 363 or send a message here <a href=\"https://www.splend.com.au/contact\">https://www.splend.com.au/contact</a><strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Splend:\r\n\r\nIf you are approved for Uber and have the required documents, then they can onboard you into a new model Splend car the same day you apply!\r\nIf you are NOT already approved for Uber, you will need to apply with Uber. You can still sign-up with Splend, and they can process your Uber application for you.\r\n\r\nTo start, fill in that short 30 seconds form on the link below and Splend team will call you to take you through the sign-up process.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Splend website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nEarning will depend on your availability, schedules, number of hours you work a week. Splend gives the calculation to show that 45h a week can earn you up to $1000 a week.','no'),(1569,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1570,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_exclusion','','no'),(1571,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1572,'options_compatibility_check_providers_11_country','AU','no'),(1573,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_11_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1574,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_logo','340','no'),(1575,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1576,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_name','Keyz','no'),(1577,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1578,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_Website','https://keyz.com.au','no'),(1579,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1580,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_potential','$1000 per week (45h)','no'),(1581,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1582,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nHere at Keyz we understand that people need a chance to succeed and have flexible options available, even those who don\'t own the car. Whether you are looking to make more money, already have a main job, or work for yourself, Keyz can help. That way, you can become your own boss, create your own hours, and start earning money.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong><strong></strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Keyz:\r\n\r\nPassport or Birth Certificate\r\nDrivers License\r\nLatest Bank Account Statement\r\n12 Months Driving History (Mandatory for Sydney, Melbourne, and Canberra Sign-Ups, unless you have a Drivers Authority Card / Driver Accreditation)\r\nDrivers Industry Card / F or T Extension (Mandatory for Brisbane and Perth Sign)\r\nScreenshot of your active Uber Account\r\nABN\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://keyz.com.au/how-to-start-earning/\">https://keyz.com.au/how-to-start-earning/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://keyz.com.au/uber-rental-cars/\">https://keyz.com.au/uber-rental-cars/</a>\r\nRequest terms and conditions from KEYZ team.\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Keyz on Brisbane: (07) 3106 8181, Sydney: (02) 8016 4789, or email info@keyz.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Keyz:\r\n\r\nYou have to fill an online application form through the link below. Before you start your form, please have the following documents photographed, scanned, or copied, as you will need them later in the sign-up process. At a minimum, they will need a photographed/scanned copy of your driver\'s license, passport/birth certificate, and your relevant state requirement documents to drive for Uber.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://keyz.com.au/application-form/\">https://keyz.com.au/application-form/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Keyz website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nEarning will depend on your availability, schedules, and a number of hours you work a week. Keyz gives the calculation to show that 45h a week can earn you up to $1000 a week.','no'),(1583,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1584,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_exclusion','','no'),(1585,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1586,'options_compatibility_check_providers_12_country','AU','no'),(1587,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_12_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1588,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_logo','342','no'),(1589,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1590,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_name','Airbnb','no'),(1591,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1592,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_Website','www.airbnb.com.au','no'),(1593,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1594,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_potential','from $30 per room / night','no'),(1595,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1596,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nAs an Airbnb host, no matter what kind of home or room you have to share, Airbnb makes it simple and secure to earn money and reach millions of travellers looking for unique places to stay, just like yours. With Airbnb, youre in full control of your availability, prices, house rules, and how you interact with guests. You can set check-in times and handle the process however you like.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Airnbn:\r\n\r\nHave a spare room, house, or apartment\r\nAlight to the guidelines of the responsible hosting in Australia\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/host/homes?from_nav=1\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/host/homes?from_nav=1</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/hospitality\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/hospitality</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/help/article/1377/responsible-hosting-in-australia\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/help/article/1377/responsible-hosting-in-australia</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/help/topic/250/terms---policies\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/help/topic/250/terms---policies</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/diversity\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/diversity</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/help?from=footer\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/help?from=footer</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/terms\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/terms/privacy_policy\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/terms/privacy_policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Airnbn on +61 2 8520 3333\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Airnbn:\r\n\r\nClick on the top right corner, sign up, and start the process. Airnbn will give you 3 ways to start, you can sign up with your Facebook or Google account or simply with your email address.\r\n\r\nTo start the process, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com.au/host/homes?page=faq_article\">https://www.airbnb.com.au/host/homes?page=faq_article</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Airnbn website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nEarning will depend on your place, availability, and how often you want to host. Use Airnbn earn combability tool to calculate potential earnings in your area. You can earn as low as $30 per room every night to up to a few hundreds per room every night, or a couple of thousands for the entire place every week. It will depend on your area and your property.','no'),(1597,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1598,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_exclusion','','no'),(1599,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_13_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1600,'options_compatibility_check_providers_13_country','AU','no'),(1601,'_options_compatibil