4_logo','345','no'),(1838,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1839,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_name','Altspc','no'),(1840,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1841,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_Website','www.altspc.com','no'),(1842,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1843,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_potential','from $50 to $2,500 per month','no'),(1844,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1845,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nALTSPC is a space sharing website, similar to Airbnb, which allows users to post a space (e.g. property, hall or a chair at a barbershop) and rent it out to a \'guest\'. They provide a $60 million insurance cover, professional photography, and networking services.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with ALTSPC:\r\n\r\nIt depends on what kind of space you have. First, you sign up, take photos of your space, and then enter the space size and what you are hoping to accomplish. Then the ALTSPC team will review your space and if accepted, you\'ll be ready to go.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.altspc.com/en/businesssafety\">https://www.altspc.com/en/businesssafety</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.altspc.com/end/help\">https://www.altspc.com/end/help</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.altspc.com/en/termsandconditions\">https://www.altspc.com/en/termsandconditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.altspc.com/en/insurance\">https://www.altspc.com/en/insurance</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact ALTSPC via email: support@altspc.com<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with ALTSPC:\r\n\r\nYou will need to create an account and enter your space\'s information and some photos. Once all of that is entered, the ALTSPC team will review your listing and then the process to market your space will begin.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.altspc.com/en/account/register\">https://www.altspc.com/en/account/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the ALTSPC website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepends on the size and location of your listing, but it is projected that you can make $2,500 per month.','no'),(1846,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1847,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_exclusion','','no'),(1848,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1849,'options_compatibility_check_providers_14_country','AU','no'),(1850,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_14_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1851,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_logo','348','no'),(1852,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1853,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_name','HomeAway','no'),(1854,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1855,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_Website','www.homeaway.com.au','no'),(1856,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1857,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_potential','$30 to $200 per single room','no'),(1858,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1859,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nThe HomeAway has a family of 11 brands that you can work with. HomeAway apartment, house, or room rental service that allows you to list a property and then people rent it out for a short stay. This is most advantageous for people near scenic landmarks.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with HomeAway:\r\n\r\nAll you need is an available place to rent out a room, apartment, or house.\r\nYou also need to align with the terms and conditions of renting out.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/homeaway-au/security-centre\">https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/homeaway-au/security-centre</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/about-us/legal/terms-conditions.html\">https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/about-us/legal/terms-conditions.html</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/about-us/legal/privacy-policy.html\">https://www.homeaway.com.au/info/about-us/legal/privacy-policy.html</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact HomeAway on 1800 662 594\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with HomeAway:\r\n\r\nYou will have to create an account online and follow the instruction on the form. You will have to upload photos of the place you want to rent out and, of course, your address. The team will then review your listing and if accepted, you will be entered into the site, ready to be found by millions of people all over the world.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homeaway.com.au/lyp\">https://www.homeaway.com.au/lyp</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the HomeAway website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYour earning will depend on the home and location, you can receive an estimate once you create an account. You can expect anything from $30 per single room to $200 and more a night for an entire place.','no'),(1860,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1861,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_exclusion','','no'),(1862,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1863,'options_compatibility_check_providers_15_country','AU','no'),(1864,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_15_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1865,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_logo','351','no'),(1866,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1867,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_name','Flatmates','no'),(1868,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1869,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_Website','https://flatmates.com.au/','no'),(1870,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1871,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_potential','$200 a week in average ','no'),(1872,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1873,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nFlatmates is home sharing website that allows homeowners to rent out their spare rooms on a more permanent basis to people who post their own profiles on the website. You can choose, on the website, a profile you like the most and contact that person if they are looking for a room in your area.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Flatmates:\r\n\r\nAll you need is a spare room, granny flat, or house that you want to rent out.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/info\">https://flatmates.com.au/info</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/info/frequently-asked-questions\">https://flatmates.com.au/info/frequently-asked-questions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/info/how-does-it-work\">https://flatmates.com.au/info/how-does-it-work</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/info/terms\">https://flatmates.com.au/info/terms</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Flatmates via this link below: <a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/contact\">https://flatmates.com.au/contact</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Flatmates:\r\n\r\nYou need to create an account and list your room or flat for people willing to share a home with others, you will need to upload photos and provide the address. Follow the link below to create an account.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://flatmates.com.au/list-place\">https://flatmates.com.au/list-place</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Flatmates website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nIt all depends on the room size and location. In capital cities, you can rent your spare single room for more than $200 a week.','no'),(1874,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1875,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_exclusion','','no'),(1876,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1877,'options_compatibility_check_providers_16_country','AU','no'),(1878,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_16_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1881,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_111.67.5.164','1538223663','no'),(1882,'_transient_external_ip_address_111.67.5.164','111.67.5.164','no'),(1891,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_137.226.113.27','1538242320','no'),(1892,'_transient_external_ip_address_137.226.113.27','111.67.5.164','no'),(1900,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_51.38.81.241','1538253081','no'),(1901,'_transient_external_ip_address_51.38.81.241','111.67.5.164','no'),(1904,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_52.53.201.78','1538260967','no'),(1905,'_transient_external_ip_address_52.53.201.78','111.67.5.164','no'),(1908,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_40.77.193.97','1538264998','no'),(1909,'_transient_external_ip_address_40.77.193.97','111.67.5.164','no'),(1915,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_logo','354','no'),(1916,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1917,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_name','Auzzie Families','no'),(1918,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1919,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_Website','https://auzziefamilies.com','no'),(1920,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1921,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_potential','$330 per student','no'),(1922,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1923,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nAuzzie Families allows you to take in a student, take care of certain needs, and possibly have them intern with you. This allows a child or student to experience Family life in Australia. There are certain rules a career must follow like taking the \"Ward\" out every month, assisting them in opening a bank account, assisting with adapting to life in Australia. The career is not financially responsible for the student.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Auzzie Families:\r\n\r\nAll hosts in NSW must hold a valid Working with Children check (WWCC) if hosting students aged under 18 years. A WWCC is also required for anyone else living in the home aged over 18. Auzzie Families recommends that the host contact their insurance provider to ensure they are covered by the correct policy for their situation. Please note that not all policies would cover a student living in your home. This program is currently open for Sydney and Brisbane only. For more information about day to daycare for students, pls follow the link below.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/auzzie-families-guardians-program/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/auzzie-families-guardians-program/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/auzzie-families-guardians-program/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/auzzie-families-guardians-program/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/homestay-australia-sydney-brisbane/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/homestay-australia-sydney-brisbane/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/rules-and-regulations/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/rules-and-regulations/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Auzzie Families at 2 9804 4700\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Auzzie Families, you need to chose an application for your city and follow online form registration, see link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/application-forms/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/application-forms/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Auzzie Families website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn $330 for student hosting per week, see link below for more details.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://auzziefamilies.com/tariff/sydney-2018-public-private-high-schools/\">https://auzziefamilies.com/tariff/sydney-2018-public-private-high-schools/</a>','no'),(1924,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1925,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_exclusion','','no'),(1926,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1927,'options_compatibility_check_providers_17_country','AU','no'),(1928,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_17_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1929,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_logo','359','no'),(1930,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1931,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_name','Oz Homestay','no'),(1932,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1933,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_Website','www.ozhomestay.com.au','no'),(1934,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1935,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_potential','$300-$310 per hosted person','no'),(1936,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1937,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nOz Homestay is a private home accepting overseas students to live as a part of the family, a homestay host can be an individual, couple, or family.\r\nBeing a homestay host provides great insights into other cultures and can be a very rewarding cultural exchange experience with a small financial remuneration. Life-long friendships are often established through the process. It is not a matter of simply renting out a room in your house.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Oz Homestay:\r\n\r\nCarers/ hosts and their adult household members are required to obtain a Working With Children Check. You can apply for this in your state government.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-registration-procedures/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-registration-procedures/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/standard-of-homestay-requirements/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/standard-of-homestay-requirements/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/carer-responsibilities/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/carer-responsibilities/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-faqs/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-faqs/</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/conditions-and-cancellation-policy/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/conditions-and-cancellation-policy/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information please contact Oz Homestay on 02 9325 6988 or E-mail: info@ozhomestay.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Oz Homestay:\r\n\r\nComplete Registration Form and complete The Working With Children Check Form. Once you have completed your application, you will receive a Working With Children Check Application Number. Please inform Oz Homestay of this number so they can verify that you have a valid application in progress. Once your application has been processed, you will be notified of the outcome by email (or post if you do not have an email address). There are only two results of a Working With Children Checka clearance or a bar. Follow the links below to start registration.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-registration-procedures/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-registration-procedures/</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ozhomestay.org/register/household/register\">https://ozhomestay.org/register/household/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Oz Homestay website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn $300-$310 per person hosted every week, see all information in this link below:\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-fees-and-conditions/\">http://www.ozhomestay.com.au/families/host-family-fees-and-conditions/</a>','no'),(1938,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1939,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_exclusion','','no'),(1940,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1941,'options_compatibility_check_providers_18_country','AU','no'),(1942,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_18_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1943,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_logo','364','no'),(1944,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1945,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_name','Home Care Heroes','no'),(1946,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1947,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_Website','www.homecareheroes.com.au','no'),(1948,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1949,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_potential',' $32 per hour','no'),(1950,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1951,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nHome Care Heroes is a website that connects carers with people in need. Here, they promise to find the right carer for the elderly and disabled. They offer more of a spending time with those in need than a technical approach to caring for the elderly and disabled.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Home Care Heroes:\r\n\r\nA valid ABN and the right to work in Australia. 3 references who can vouch for you, to be available to work for at least 8 months, a police check (less than 2 years old) with NO disclosable court outcomes.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/onboardings/new\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/onboardings/new</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/faq\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/terms\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/privacy\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/privacy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/insurance_policy\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/insurance_policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Home Care Heroes at 02 8310 7531 or <a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/contact\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/contact</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Home Care Heroes:\r\n\r\nYou need an ABN, A Police Check and 3 references. If they accept you then you can start an account and allow others to find you. To start, fill in the application at the bottom of this page:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/onboardings/new\">https://www.homecareheroes.com.au/onboardings/new</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Home Care Heroes website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn $32 per hour.','no'),(1952,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1953,'options_compatibility_check_providers_19_exclusion','','no'),(1954,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_19_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1955,'options_compatibility_check_provide