art with Hireup:\r\n\r\nYou register on the website under the link below, then their team speaks with two referees and verifies your personal ID, a Police Criminal Record check, a Working with Children/Vulnerable People check (if applicable), a CPR and/or First Aid certificate, and a current rsum. Then you create a profile, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://app.hireup.com.au/#/register\">https://app.hireup.com.au/#/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Hireup: website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nThe Hireup standard pay rate is $31.55 (including superannuation)','no'),(1980,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_21_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1981,'options_compatibility_check_providers_21_exclusion','','no'),(1982,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_21_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1983,'options_compatibility_check_providers_21_country','AU','no'),(1984,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_21_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1985,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_logo','373','no'),(1986,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(1987,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_name','Care Seekers','no'),(1988,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(1989,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_Website','www.careseekers.com.au','no'),(1990,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(1991,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_potential','$25-$35 per hour','no'),(1992,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(1993,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nCareseekers is a digital platform that connects individuals, families, and organisations to care and support workers. Their focus is aged, disability, and post-operative care.\r\nCareseekers gives you choice and control over the work you do. Working as an independent contractor, you set your hourly rates and choose the work that suits your schedule. Careseekers is using digital technology to directly connect more than 1,200 skilled, qualified care workers with people who need care; making it easier to find affordable in-home care.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Careseekers:\r\n\r\nAn Australian police check obtained within the last 12 months\r\nThe names and contact details of two referees\r\n100 points ID\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/carer/resources/tools\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/carer/resources/tools</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/insurance-policy\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/insurance-policy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/careworker-faqs\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/careworker-faqs</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/terms-conditions\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/terms-conditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/privacy-policy\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Careseekers on 1300 765 465\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Careseekers:\r\n\r\nCreate your care worker profile for free, Provide an Australian police check obtained within the last 12 months, The names and contact details of two referees, 100 points ID. Wait to be contacted by the team to see if you have been accepted. To start follow the registration form below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.careseekers.com.au/carer\">https://www.careseekers.com.au/carer</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Careseekers website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nMost care workers charge between $25-$35 per hour on weekdays.','no'),(1994,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(1995,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_exclusion','','no'),(1996,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(1997,'options_compatibility_check_providers_22_country','AU','no'),(1998,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_22_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(1999,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_185.234.218.55','1538270124','no'),(2000,'_transient_external_ip_address_185.234.218.55','111.67.5.164','no'),(2002,'options_compatibility_check_providers_23_logo','376','no'),(2003,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_23_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2004,'options_compatibility_check_providers_23_name','Mad Paws','no'),(2005,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_23_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2006,'options_compatibility_check_providers_23_Website','www.madpaws.com.au','no'),(2007,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_23_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2008,'options_compatibility_check_providers_23_potential','$20-$40 per day','no'),(2009,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_23_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2010,'options_compatibility_check_providers_23_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nMad Paws is a Sydney-based startup that was created to fill in the ever growing need in the pet boarding market for affordable and local pet accommodation whilst still maintaining the care, love, and attention pets receive at high-end, expensive, pet boarding services. The way it works is that you find trusted and caring pet sitters in your neighbourhood via the mad paws platform. Meet &amp; Greet your pet sitter and book a stay in their house or yours.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Mad Paws:\r\n\r\nYou must finish an online training course which takes 40 mins, and you must have referees.\r\nFollow the information and instruction on the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://help.madpaws.com.au/support/solutions/articles/9000060128-how-does-mad-paws-verify-their-pet-sitters-\">https://help.madpaws.com.au/support/solutions/articles/9000060128-how-does-mad-paws-verify-their-pet-sitters-</a>\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.madpaws.com.au/support/home\">https://help.madpaws.com.au/support/home</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.madpaws.com.au/become-a-sitter\">https://www.madpaws.com.au/become-a-sitter</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.madpaws.com.au/about\">https://www.madpaws.com.au/about</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Mad Paws on 02 8046 6536 or email: service@madpaws.com.au<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Mad Paws:\r\n\r\nCreate a profile, finish the registration process, and finish their 40-minute training course. You\'ll then have testimonials about your dog sitting skills ready to post on the profile. You can create your profile with email or Facebook, to start follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.madpaws.com.au/sign-in\">https://www.madpaws.com.au/sign-in</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Mad Paws website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nRates will depend on if you are pet walking or pet sitting. On average, you can earn $20-$40 per day','no'),(2011,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_23_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2012,'optio