e. During the Sign Up process theyll guide you on how to make your Sitter profile stand out from the crowd. Once you\'ve completed your profile, they will review your listing and approve your profile. They will send you an email within 24 hours to update you on the status of this review, and to let you know if more information is needed for us to approve your profile. Create a free profile and set your rates, Complete your verification and gain badges, Set up your calendar, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.petsleepover.com.au/become-a-sitter\">http://www.petsleepover.com.au/become-a-sitter</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the PetSleepover website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn over $1000 a month, all depends on your circumstances, commitment and availability.','no'),(2039,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_25_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2040,'options_compatibility_check_providers_25_exclusion','','no'),(2041,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_25_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2042,'options_compatibility_check_providers_25_country','AU','no'),(2043,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_25_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2044,'options_compatibility_check_providers_26_logo','387','no'),(2045,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_26_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2046,'options_compatibility_check_providers_26_name','Urbanyou','no'),(2047,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_26_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2048,'options_compatibility_check_providers_26_Website','https://urbanyou.com.au','no'),(2049,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_26_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2050,'options_compatibility_check_providers_26_potential','$25 to $40 per hour','no'),(2051,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_26_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2052,'options_compatibility_check_providers_26_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nUrbanYou is a two-ways marketplace, they have clients that need jobs/tasks done and they look for new workers who can deliver that tasks. UrbanYou works with the best cleaners and gardeners, people who know how to do it and have some sort of experience. They are a network of trusted and reliable service providers. You sign up as a Pro (professional cleaner or gardener), choose when you want to work, and how much. Build up your business or simply accept a few jobs on-demand on the side. UrbanYou is not an employer but simply connects independent service professionals with customers.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with UrbanYou:\r\n\r\nBe physically active/healthy.\r\nDemonstrate your experience in cleaning or gardening, minimum 2-years experience\r\nPublic liability insurance (they can help you sort this out)\r\nPass their background checks, including Police Check.\r\nPassion for going the extra mile to maintain their 100% satisfaction guarantee.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/become_pro\">https://urbanyou.com.au/become_pro</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/services\">https://urbanyou.com.au/services</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/help\">https://urbanyou.com.au/help</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/trust\">https://urbanyou.com.au/trust</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/terms\">https://urbanyou.com.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://urbanyou.com.au/privacy\">https://urbanyou.com.au/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact UrbanYou on 1300 048 566.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start working with UrbanYou:\r\n\r\nYou need to 