rt browsing through tasks that you\'re able to complete. Make an offer on a task and tell the Poster why you\'re the best person to complete the task. If the task has been successfully assigned to you, you will be able to start a conversation with the Poster via private messaging and arrange further details about completing the task.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Airtasker:\r\n\r\nYou need to have the ability and skills to complete the task that you are pitching for.\r\nYou have to follow the Tasker guidelines, see the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/community-guidelines-worker/\">https://www.airtasker.com/community-guidelines-worker/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong><strong></strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/how-it-works/\">https://www.airtasker.com/how-it-works/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/earn-money/\">https://www.airtasker.com/earn-money/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.airtasker.com/hc/en-us/\">https://support.airtasker.com/hc/en-us/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/community-guidelines/\">https://www.airtasker.com/community-guidelines/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/terms/\">https://www.airtasker.com/terms/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/privacy/\">https://www.airtasker.com/privacy/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Airtasker via the below link:\r\n<a href=\"https://support.airtasker.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\">https://support.airtasker.com/hc/en-us/requests/new</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Airtasker:\r\n\r\nYou have to create a free account. You can sign up using your email or Facebook account.\r\nAfter you sign up, be sure to complete your profile by selecting the settings tab under your account. You\'ll be able to add details such as skills, verifications, portfolio attachments and manage your alerts. Follow the link below to sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.airtasker.com/sign-up/\">https://www.airtasker.com/sign-up/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Airtasker website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nWith Airtasker you can earn an average of $25 per hour, this will vary with task complexity and required skills.','no'),(2067,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_27_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2068,'options_compatibility_check_providers_27_exclusion','','no'),(2069,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_27_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2070,'options_compatibility_check_providers_27_country','AU','no'),(2071,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_27_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2072,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_logo','393','no'),(2073,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2074,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_name','Sidekicker','no'),(2075,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2076,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_Website','www.sidekicker.com.au','no'),(2077,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2078,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_potential','$20 to $30 per hour','no'),(2079,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2080,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nSidekicker is an on-demand staffing platform that is used by the likes of Uber, Rydges, and Seek to hire qualified staff to complete hourly or daily jobs. They are looking for workers in events, hospitality, promotions, retail, and business administration that can be accessed via their online platform. For Sidekicks, they offer a flexible way to make money, gain experience, and take control over when and where they work. All Sidekicks will be screened by their team and are able to apply for jobs via their mobile app.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Sidekicker:\r\n\r\nYou need to apply online and tell them about all of that awesome experience youve accumulated. Then, when selected, come in for an onboarding session with them.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sidekicker.com.au/work/\">https://www.sidekicker.com.au/work/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sidekicker.com.au/skplus-terms-of-use/\">https://www.sidekicker.com.au/skplus-terms-of-use/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://intercom.help/sidekicker\">https://intercom.help/sidekicker</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sidekicker.com.au/skplus-terms-of-use/\">https://www.sidekicker.com.au/skplus-terms-of-use/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.sidekicker.com.au/privacy-policy/\">https://www.sidekicker.com.au/privacy-policy/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Sidekicker via email: support@sidekicker.com.au<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Sidekicker:\r\n\r\nYou have to fill in an online form and create your account. You will have to tell them about your experience in your account, and once you are selected Sidekicker will contact you for the onboarding. To sign up, follow this link:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.getsidekicker.com/create-sidekick-account\">https://www.getsidekicker.com/create-sidekick-account</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Sidekicker website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn from $20 to $30 per hour, this will vary with task complexity and required skills.','no'),(2081,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2082,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_exclusion','','no'),(2083,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2084,'options_compatibility_check_providers_28_country','AU','no'),(2085,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_28_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2088,'options_compatibility_check_providers_29_logo','396','no'),(2089,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_29_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2090,'options_compatibility_check_providers_29_name','Squaddle','no'),(2091,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_29_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2092,'options_compatibility_check_providers_29_Website','www.squaddle.com','no'),(2093,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_29_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2094,'options_compatibility_check_providers_29_potential','$20 per hour ','no'),(2095,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_29_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2096,'options_compatibility_check_providers_29_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nSquaddle is an app that connects hospitality businesses with independent contractors for work on-demand. Using Squaddle, contractors can select from local businesses that are rated by peers and seeking bar staff, wait staff, chefs, kitchen hands, baristas, or just about any other short-term hospitality need.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Squaddle:\r\n\r\nTo sign-up with Squaddle, you need to be over 18 years of age, have a tax file number, and an Australian Business Number (ABN).\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply w