ss\' at the top of the page. Once you publish the listing, you will be able to view and edit the listing in \'Your Listings\' in your Dashboard.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Designerex: website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou set your own prices for your listings. The Designerex: service fee ranges between 16% and 25%, depending on the total transaction amount. You can earn from $5 to a couple of hundreds per item.','no'),(2167,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_34_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2168,'options_compatibility_check_providers_34_exclusion','a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"male\";}','no'),(2169,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_34_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2170,'options_compatibility_check_providers_34_country','AU','no'),(2171,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_34_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2172,'options_compatibility_check_providers_35_logo','415','no'),(2173,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_35_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2174,'options_compatibility_check_providers_35_name','Spacer','no'),(2175,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_35_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2176,'options_compatibility_check_providers_35_Website','www.spacer.com.au','no'),(2177,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_35_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2178,'options_compatibility_check_providers_35_potential','up to $350 per month','no'),(2179,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_35_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2180,'options_compatibility_check_providers_35_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nSpacer is an online marketplace for space, connecting people with extra space (Hosts) to those looking for storage space (Renters). At Spacer, they are about utilising and sharing local resources to meet a need in the community. Your space, your storage solutions can come in all shapes and sizes and should be convenie