tart:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.boatsetter.com/users/sign_up\">https://www.boatsetter.com/users/sign_up</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Boatsetter website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nIt will depend on your boat, you can earn from $500 a day to $15000 a month or even $50000 a year.','no'),(2209,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_37_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2210,'options_compatibility_check_providers_37_exclusion','','no'),(2211,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_37_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2212,'options_compatibility_check_providers_37_country','AU','no'),(2213,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_37_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2214,'options_compatibility_check_providers_38_logo','424','no'),(2215,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_38_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2216,'options_compatibility_check_providers_38_name','Camplify','no'),(2217,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_38_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2218,'options_compatibility_check_providers_38_Website','www.camplify.com.au','no'),(2219,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_38_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2220,'options_compatibility_check_providers_38_potential','from $280 to $2100 per week','no'),(2221,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_38_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2222,'options_compatibility_check_providers_38_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nCamplify is proud to be Australia\'s largest caravan hire and RV peer-to-peer sharing community. Their aim is to connect our owners with holidaymakers across the country looking for all types of caravans, campervans, motorhomes, and camper trailers to enjoy a getaway in. Camplify gives RV owners the opportunity to earn extra income on-demand.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Camplify:\r\n\r\nYou need a cam