lamy.com/contributor/why-alamy/best-place-to-sell-stock-imagery/\">https://www.alamy.com/contributor/why-alamy/best-place-to-sell-stock-imagery/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/terms/australia.asp\">https://www.alamy.com/terms/australia.asp</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/terms/general.asp#Our-privacy-policy\">https://www.alamy.com/terms/general.asp#Our-privacy-policy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/terms/contributor.asp\">https://www.alamy.com/terms/contributor.asp</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information please contact Alamy via email: contributors@alamy.com\r\n<h4>How to start</h4>\r\nTo start with Alamy:\r\n\r\nYou must register an account online by filling the form on the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/registration/contributor-signup.aspx\">https://www.alamy.com/registration/contributor-signup.aspx</a>\r\n\r\nTo better understand how to list your images, please read all the information on this link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/contributor/how-to-sell-images/how-do-I-get-my-images-for-sale/?section=2\">https://www.alamy.com/contributor/how-to-sell-images/how-do-I-get-my-images-for-sale/?section=2</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Alamy: website before starting.\r\n<h4>How much you can earn</h4>\r\nYou take 50% of the cost of your images sold through the Alamy website. You also have additional revenue opportunities, explore the link below for more information:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.alamy.com/contributor/how-to-sell-images/additional-revenue-options/?section=10\">https://www.alamy.com/contributor/how-to-sell-images/additional-revenue-options/?section=10</a>','no'),(2283,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_42_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2284,'options_compatibility_check_providers_42_exclusion','','no'),(2285,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_42_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2286,'options_compatibility_check_providers_42_country','AU','no'),(2287,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_42_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2288,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_logo','441','no'),(2289,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2290,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_name','Contena','no'),(2291,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2292,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_Website','www.contena.co','no'),(2293,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2294,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_potential','$100-300 per article/assignment ','no'),(2295,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2296,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nContena is simply the best way to start making money from writing. They show you how to create everything you need to start a great freelance writing business and help you find the best remote and location independent writing gigs. Yes, there is a cost to join Contena. When you activate your Contena membership, you receive access to all of their resources, including Contena Academy which shows you exactly how to get started with freelance writing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Contena:\r\n\r\nYou must have a writing ability, you have to register an account and be able to pay a monthly membership fee. They have a few different plans and pricing options available to meet your needs.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://blog.contena.co/contena-faq/\">https://blog.contena.co/contena-faq/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://blog.contena.co/category/getting-started/\">https://blog.contena.co/category/getting-started/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://blog.contena.co/category/making-money/\">https://blog.contena.co/category/making-money/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.contena.co/terms\">https://www.contena.co/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.contena.co/privacy\">https://www.contena.co/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Contena via email: writers@contena.co\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Contena:\r\n\r\nFirst, you register in 3 simple steps:\r\nCreate an Account\r\nReceive Invitation\r\nActivate and Join\r\n\r\nContena requires a paid membership. We have a few different plans and pricing options available to meet your needs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.contena.co/signup\">https://www.contena.co/signup</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Contena website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou can earn as high as $100-300 per article, or you can write the whole website content and earn even around $1000 per month or more as a freelance writer. There is no minimum or maximu you can earn all depends on your time and quality you will deliver.\r\n\r\nPlease read the earnings disclaimer: <a href=\"https://www.contena.co/earnings\">https://www.contena.co/earnings</a>','no'),(2297,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2298,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_exclusion','','no'),(2299,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2300,'options_compatibility_check_providers_43_country','AU','no'),(2301,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_43_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2302,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_logo','444','no'),(2303,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2304,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_name','Fiverr','no'),(2305,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2306,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_Website','www.fiverr.com','no'),(2307,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2308,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_potential','starts at $5 per project/task','no'),(2309,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2310,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nFiverr is a global online marketplace offering tasks and services, beginning at a cost of $5 per job, hence its name. The site is primarily used by freelancers who use Fiverr to offer services to customers on a global scale. Services are in writing, design, website development, stagiest, and many more. You work as a freelancer and work from home or your own office.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Fiverr:\r\n\r\nJust need a skill in one of the Fiverr categories to provide service, copywriting, copy editing, proofreading, e-book development, whitepapers development are all the great opportunity for writers to make money on demand. In addition to that, you need to create a profile on Fiverr and have your bank account or PayPal account attached to it to accept payments.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://sellers.fiverr.com/en/article/how-to-start-selling-on-fiverr\">https://sellers.fiverr.com/en/article/how-to-start-selling-on-fiverr</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://sellers.fiverr.com/en/\">https://sellers.fiverr.com/en/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/terms_of_service?source=footer\">https://www.fiverr.com/terms_of_service?source=footer</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/privacy-policy?source=footer\">https://www.fiverr.com/privacy-policy?source=footer</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.fiverr.com/\">https://support.fiverr.com/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/trust_safety?source=footer\">https://www.fiverr.com/trust_safety?source=footer</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Fiverr via the link below: <a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/support_tickets/new?source=help_center\">https://www.fiverr.com/support_tickets/new?source=help_center</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Fiverr:\r\n\r\nSigning up for Fiverr is free. First, you will need to create your seller profile. Your profile is how you present yourself to the community. You are encouraged to present yourself in a professional manner. Then your Gig is the service that you sell on Fiverr. Creating your Gig is an opportunity to show off your talent and provide buyers with all the information they need to help them decide to do business with you.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/start_selling\">https://www.fiverr.com/start_selling</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Fiverr website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nOn Fiverr, your earnings start at $5 per project/ task completed and more, this will depend on your rating by buyers, your skills, your profile and kind of the service you are providing. On average, you can earn from $5 to a couple of hundreds a week.','no'),(2311,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2312,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_exclusion','','no'),(2313,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2314,'options_compatibility_check_providers_44_country','AU','no'),(2315,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_44_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2316,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_logo','447','no'),(2317,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2318,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_name','Upwork','no'),(2319,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2320,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_Website','www.upwork.com','no'),(2321,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2322,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_potential','form $20 to more /per task','no'),(2323,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2324,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nUpwork is a global freelancing platform where businesses and independent professionals connect and collaborate remotely. You can work as a freelancer and work from home. There is a wide variety of available projects across multiple categories, the copywriting category is highly rated in Upwork.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Upwork:\r\n\r\nYou need to have marketable copywriting skill on Upwork, you choose your own clients and copywriting projects. You have to complete your profile and they will highlight the ideal jobs for you. Also, search projects, and respond to client invitations.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/cat/writing/\">https://www.upwork.com/cat/writing/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/i/how-it-works/freelancer/\">https://www.upwork.com/i/how-it-works/freelancer/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/i/how-it-works/faq/\">https://www.upwork.com/i/how-it-works/faq/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/i/trust-safety-mission/\">https://www.upwork.com/i/trust-safety-mission/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/legal#\">https://www.upwork.com/legal#</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/legal#privacy\">https://www.upwork.com/legal#privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Upwork via the link below: <a href=\"https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us\">https://support.upwork.com/hc/en-us</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Upwork:\r\n\r\nYou need to register an account and fill out your skills and experience. Successful freelancers have profiles that are complete, accurate, and paint a compelling picture of your services, skills, and accomplishments. Your profile is an opportunity to advertise your freelance business to potential clients. A 100% complete profile is required if youd like to achieve Rising Talent status, Top Rated status and access to Premium Services. You can find your profile completion percentage on the right-hand panel of your Find Work page under My Profile. To start registration, follow the link below.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/signup/?dest=home\">https://www.upwork.com/signup/?dest=home</a>\r\n\r\nAfter you submit, they will notify you of their decision within 24 hours.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Upwork website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepends on the job and level of skills you have. It can be an hourly rate or a fixed price. Eg. you can earn from $20 or more per hour to $500 per project fixed price fee.','no'),(2325,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2326,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_exclusion','','no'),(2327,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2328,'options_compatibility_check_providers_45_country','AU','no'),(2329,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_45_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2330,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_logo','450','no'),(2331,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2332,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_name','GoLance','no'),(2333,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2334,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_Website','https://golance.com','no'),(2335,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2336,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_potential','$20 to $250 per project','no'),(2337,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2338,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nGoLance is a complete online workforce platform that makes it easy for you to do what you do best. GoLance mission is to make life easier for online workers and employers by offering greater flexibility, equality, and efficiency. Their site is designed to work equally in helping business owners, part-time freelancers, and those who use job sites as a main source of income. They provide great opportunity to take advantage of your lifetime general administration skills.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with GoLance:\r\n\r\nYou need to have a skill in at least one of those categories in order to provide a general administration service: Accounting &amp; Consulting, Admin Support, Customer Service, Data Science &amp; Analytics, Design &amp; Creative, Engineering &amp; Architecture, IT &amp; Networking, Legal, Sales &amp; Marketing, Translation, Web &amp; Mobile &amp; Software Development, and Writing.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/how-it-works\">https://golance.com/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/how-it-works/faq\">https://golance.com/how-it-works/faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/terms-of-service\">https://golance.com/terms-of-service</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/privacy-policy\">https://golance.com/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact GoLance on support@golance.com<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with GoLance:\r\n\r\nIts as simple as filling out a profile including past jobs, results of skills tests, and portfolio items. Once your profile is complete, you are ready to start searching for work!\r\n\r\nTo start follow the link below:\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/signup\">https://golance.com/signup</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the GoLance website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nGoLance keeps fees simple for users with a standard 10% commission fee deducted from every project payment. Once you have fulfilled the job requirements and the client is happy, your payment will be submitted. You have agreed to the rate if your contract is hourly you will get paid weekly. If your contract is a fixed price you will get paid at the end of each milestone. Globally in average freelancers earn from $20 to $250 per project and sometimes per hour if they are experts.\r\n\r\nThere are different options of payment and billing, follow the link below for more information:\r\n<a href=\"https://golance.com/payment-and-billing\">https://golance.com/payment-and-billing</a>','no'),(2339,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2340,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_exclusion','','no'),(2341,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2342,'options_compatibility_check_providers_46_country','AU','no'),(2343,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_46_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2344,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_logo','454','no'),(2345,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2346,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_name','Freelance-market','no'),(2347,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2348,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_Website','www.freelance-market.com.au','no'),(2349,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2350,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_potential','$5-$50 an hour','no'),(2351,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2352,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nFreelance-Market is the marketplace for all Australian contractors and clients. You sign up as a contractor and get offered jobs by clients finding specialised work.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Freelance-Market.\r\n\r\nFor your general administration skills, explore all jobs under this category: Admin Support and Customer Service.\r\nFreelance-Market charges you a one-off fee every time they place an introduction. To prove the seriousness of your entry, they charge a one-off registration fee of twice your hourly rate AU$80 + GST.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all therequirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/faq\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/tac\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/tac</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/docs\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/docs</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/doc/FM-AU-TAC.pdf\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/doc/FM-AU-TAC.pdf</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Freelance-Market via email: info@freelance-market.com.au or +61-2-5592 7526\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Freelance-Market:\r\n\r\nYou must fill in the online application for as a contractor and pay the $80 registration fee.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/registration\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/registration</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Freelance-Market website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nFor administration skills, you can earn anything from $5-$50 an hour. Hourly rates for each profession are listed on the home page on the left side, see link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelance-market.com.au/\">https://www.freelance-market.com.au/</a>','no'),(2353,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2354,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_exclusion','','no'),(2355,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2356,'options_compatibility_check_providers_47_country','AU','no'),(2357,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_47_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2358,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_logo','458','no'),(2359,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2360,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_name','Freelancer','no'),(2361,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2362,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_Website','www.freelancer.com.au','no'),(2363,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2364,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_potential','$20 to $250 per project','no'),(2365,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2366,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nFreelancer is the world\'s largest freelancing and crowdsourcing marketplace by a number of users and projects. They connect millions of employers and freelancers globally from over 247 countries, regions and territories. Through their marketplace, employers can hire freelancers to do work in areas such as software development, writing, data entry and design right through to engineering, the sciences, sales and marketing, accounting and legal services.\r\n\r\nFreelancer Limited is trading on the Australian Securities Exchange under the ticker ASX:FLN\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Freelancer:\r\n\r\nYou must have a general administration skill and basic computing or customer service. You need to register, you need a bank account or PayPal account to accept payment, ideally, you also need some examples of previous work to create your profile. For your general administration skills, explore all jobs under this category: Business, Accounting, Human Resources &amp; Legal.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/info/how-it-works\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/info/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/about/terms\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/about/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/dmca/\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/dmca/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/info/codeofconduct\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/info/codeofconduct</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/about/privacy\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/about/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Freelancer via live Support service located at the bottom of this page: <a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/support/freelancer/general/\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/support/freelancer/general/</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Freelancer:\r\n\r\nYou create a profile by registering your email address and entering your skills and previous work, then you can start bidding on work. Follow the link and instructions to sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com.au/signup\">https://www.freelancer.com.au/signup</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Freelancer website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepends on the fixed price set by the bids that have been accepted. Globally, on average freelancers earn from $20 to $250 per project an hour if they are experts.','no'),(2367,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2368,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_exclusion','','no'),(2369,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2370,'options_compatibility_check_providers_48_country','AU','no'),(2371,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_48_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2372,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_logo','459','no'),(2373,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2374,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_name','99deigns','no'),(2375,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2376,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_Website','https://99designs.com.au','no'),(2377,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2378,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_potential','$20 to $250 per project','no'),(2379,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2380,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nThe most trusted source for custom graphic design online! A client asks 99designs to design them a logo/website/app. The client can then choose their favourite design. In some cases the client will shortlist 6 designers who can work together or tweak their designs a little. When the client picks a design the designer must hand over .psd .jpeg .swf etc.. You need to have design skills and experience to be able to provide service on this marketplace and earn money.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with 99designs:\r\n\r\nYou must have digital design skills. You need to register, you need a bank account or PayPal account to accept payment, ideally you also need some examples of previous work to create your profile.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all therequirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/designers\">https://99designs.com.au/designers</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/how-it-works\">https://99designs.com.au/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/legal/terms-of-use\">https://99designs.com.au/legal/terms-of-use</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/legal/privacy\">https://99designs.com.au/legal/privacy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.99designs.com/hc/en-us\">https://support.99designs.com/hc/en-us</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information please contact 99designs via the link below: <a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/about/contact\">https://99designs.com.au/about/contact</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with 99designs:\r\n\r\nYou create a free profile and upload your previous work experience to make this stand out.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://99designs.com.au/signup?from=%2Fuser%2Fgetstarted\">https://99designs.com.au/signup?from=%2Fuser%2Fgetstarted</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the 99Designs website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepends on the job and the contest you joined and what fees clients are willing to pay/ what package you are working on. If you are an experienced designer in average you can earn a couple of hundred per week or thousands per month. Earnings will depend on your experience and your profile portfolio. 99designs its a contest based platform so its not always guaranteed especially because clients might have different tastes. Globally, on average freelancers earn from $20 to $250 per project an hour if they are experts.','no'),(2381,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2382,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_exclusion','','no'),(2383,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2384,'options_compatibility_check_providers_49_country','AU','no'),(2385,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_49_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2386,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_logo','462','no'),(2387,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2388,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_name','Design Crowd','no'),(2389,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2390,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_Website','www.designcrowd.com','no'),(2391,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2392,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_potential','$100 is the minimum prize amount','no'),(2393,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2394,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nDesignCrowd is an online marketplace offering logo, website, print and graphic design services by providing access to freelance graphic designers and design studios around the world who work on-demand.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with DesignCrowd :\r\n\r\nYou must have digital design skills. You need to register, you need a bank account or PayPal account to accept payment. Ideally, you also need some samples of previous work to create your profile.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/how-it-works\">https://www.designcrowd.com/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/about\">https://www.designcrowd.com/about</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/help\">https://www.designcrowd.com/help</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/user-agreement\">https://www.designcrowd.com/user-agreement</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/privacy\">https://www.designcrowd.com/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact DesignCrowd on 1800 22 80 20 or <a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/contact\">https://www.designcrowd.com/contact</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with DesignCrowd:\r\n\r\nRegister an account as a designer, complete your profile.\r\nTake a look at the open jobs on their site and start submitting to ones you want to work on.\r\nOnce you find a project you are interested in, simply visit the job page and click on the \"Submit Your Design\" button. To start registration, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.designcrowd.com/registration\">https://www.designcrowd.com/registration</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the DesignCrowd website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nAs a designer, your earnings from a given project depends on:\r\nThe monetary value of the \"place payment\" (1st, 2nd, 3rd, etc)\r\nThe monetary value of the \"participation payment\"\r\nDesignCrowd\'s fees. DesignCrowd charges a standard 15% commission on all project earnings to all designers.\r\n\r\nWhen adding a \'place payment\' (e.g. 2nd place) the minimum prize amount is $100. Designs awarded 2nd place will have their files and any copyright transferred to the client as if they were awarded 1st place.','no'),(2395,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2396,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_exclusion','','no'),(2397,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2398,'options_compatibility_check_providers_50_country','AU','no'),(2399,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_50_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2400,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_logo','465','no'),(2401,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2402,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_name','OzLance','no'),(2403,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2404,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_Website','https://ozlance.com.au','no'),(2405,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2406,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_potential','$50-$250 per project','no'),(2407,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2408,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nOzLance is a catalyst for clients and Australian and New Zealand Freelancers to create mutually beneficial, equitable freelance working arrangements based on expertise, quality, price, and convenience. They\'ve found the happy medium between low-cost freelance fees and high-quality results and provide a place for clients to meet and select the right worker. OzLance freelancers compete on quality and credentials, rather than by price alone so that clients can receive a better product or service.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with OzLance:\r\n\r\nYou must have design skills and a solid credential to get more work. You need to register, you need a bank account or PayPal account to accept payment. Ideally, you also need some examples of previous work to create your profile.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong><strong></strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ozlance.com.au/how-it-works\">https://ozlance.com.au/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://ozlance.com.au/faq/freelancer\">https://ozlance.com.au/faq/freelancer</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://ozlance.com.au/terms\">https://ozlance.com.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://ozlance.com.au/privacy\">https://ozlance.com.au/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact OzLance via help centre.\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong><strong></strong></h4>\r\nTo start with OzLance:\r\n\r\nYou need to register an account and complete your profile before searching for a job. To start, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ozlance.com.au/register\">https://ozlance.com.au/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the OzLance website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nOzLance doesn\'t condone the $1 an hour culture of other freelance sites because they know better than anyone that you get what you pay for. At OzLance, they expect freelancers to charge a happy medium. Ozlance charge per project, you costing this up e.g. you can earn anything from $50-$250 per project or even a couple of thousands if the project is large and you are an expert.','no'),(2409,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2410,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_exclusion','','no'),(2411,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2412,'options_compatibility_check_providers_51_country','AU','no'),(2413,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_51_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2421,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_logo','468','no'),(2422,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2423,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_name','The Freelance Collective ','no'),(2424,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2425,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_Website','https://thefreelancecollective.com.au','no'),(2426,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2427,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_potential','$20 to $250 per project','no'),(2428,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2429,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nThe Freelance Collective is an online community of Australian freelance creatives. Theyre here to promote their skills, to build relationships with clients, and for support. There are Australian freelance bloggers, photographers, journalists, graphic designers, web developers, social media marketing gurus and more. The freelancers listed are vetted for quality, so businesses can be sure that theyre awesome at what they do. You need to subscribe to paid membership service to earn on demand.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with The Freelance collective:\r\n\r\nYou must have one of the skills that match the category they work under so that you can provide the service. You should also have a credential to get more work. You need to register, you need a bank account or PayPal account to accept payment. Ideally, you also need some samples of previous work to create your profile. Its a paid subscription service, $9/month for them to host your profile, deducted from your PayPal account each month. Or, sign up for 12 months for $99.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/how-it-works/\">https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/how-it-works/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/faq/\">https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/faq/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/legal-terms/\">https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/legal-terms/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact The Freelance Collective on: support@thefreelancecollective.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with The Freelance Collective:\r\n\r\nJust click on the \'Get Your Profile\' page, select a package (its a subscription service), then create your profile page. Allow a day for them to approve your profile and push it live. Once that happens, theyll introduce you to the other freelancers listed on this platform, and youre there. Give as much or as little information as you like. Theyve also created a space for you to add samples of your work, a video, your social media links, or anything else youd like to add to appeal to potential clients. to register, follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/get-your-profile/\">https://thefreelancecollective.com.au/get-your-profile/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on The Freelance Collective website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepends on the project you are working on and how you are costing up yourself. Globally, on average, freelancers earn from $20 to $250 per project and sometimes per hour if you are expert.','no'),(2430,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2431,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_exclusion','','no'),(2432,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2433,'options_compatibility_check_providers_52_country','AU','no'),(2434,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_52_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2435,'options_compatibility_check_providers_53_logo','471','no'),(2436,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_53_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2437,'options_compatibility_check_providers_53_name','CloudPeeps','no'),(2438,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_53_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2439,'options_compatibility_check_providers_53_Website','www.cloudpeeps.com','no'),(2440,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_53_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2441,'options_compatibility_check_providers_53_potential','from $30 per hour ','no'),(2442,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_53_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2443,'options_compatibility_check_providers_53_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nCloudPeeps is a community, marketplace, and platform that empowers freelancers and businesses to do their best work. They connect trusted freelancers and professional service providers with top clients, in a seamless platform that makes it easy to manage relationships, payments, and more.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with CloudPeeps:\r\n\r\nIn order to work with clients on the platform, you must be operating from one of the 25 countries that CloudPeeps currently serves as well as complete some 