ere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://theright.fit/for-talent/how-it-works\">https://theright.fit/for-talent/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://help.theright.fit/talent\">https://help.theright.fit/talent</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://theright.fit/terms-conditions\">https://theright.fit/terms-conditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://theright.fit/privacy\">https://theright.fit/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact theright.fit via email: contact@theright.fit<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with theright.fit:\r\n\r\nYou have a choice to sign up under free account or pro membership which is $10.95 per month or $99.00 per year. To create your profile, follow the link below to register:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://theright.fit/register\">https://theright.fit/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on theright.fit website before starting.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nThe minimum hourly rate for a model or actor is $95, to see full pricing opportunity, please follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://theright.fit/for-clients/pricing\">https://theright.fit/for-clients/pricing</a>','no'),(2458,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_54_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2459,'options_compatibility_check_providers_54_exclusion','','no'),(2460,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_54_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2461,'options_compatibility_check_providers_54_country','AU','no'),(2462,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_54_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2463,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_logo','478','no'),(2464,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2465,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_name','Mystery Shopper','no'),(2466,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2467,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_Website','www.mysteryshopper.com.au','no'),(2468,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2469,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_potential',' $15 to $80 per assignment','no'),(2470,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2471,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nBalancing work and home life is hard, so it is important to be able to have that little bit of extra pocket money. Mystery Shopping is an easy and convenient way to do that plus you also join a great community of like-minded people. You can become a Mystery or \"Secret\" Shopper and Earn rewards and cash for posing as a shopper and answering questionnaires and giving feedback about customer service, sales skills, products, procedures, and facilities! Imagine earning cash or rewards for dining at your favourite restaurant, shopping at retail outlets, or doing other things you would typically pay money to do!\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Mystery Shopper:\r\n\r\nIf you wish to become a Mystery Shopper, then training is very important to them, so you\'ll be expected to put in some time on their online training system and pass an exam before you start working with clients. It is completely web-based and does not require any equipment beyond your computer, web browser, and a connection to the internet. An application processing and training fee of $5.00 will be deducted from the payment for your first successful Mystery Shopping job.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/aboutus.asp\">http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/aboutus.asp</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/help.asp\">http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/help.asp</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/policy.asp\">http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/policy.asp</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Mystery Shopper at support@mysteryshopper.com.au<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Mystery Shopper:\r\n\r\nThe process of applying to start work with Mystery Shopping Online as a Mystery Shopper is as follows:\r\nGo to the online application.\r\nFill out the application thoroughly and professionally. (The application is the main method of decision making regarding shopper selection; therefore it is in your best interest that the information provided be presented proficiently.)\r\nYour application will be reviewed and kept in their database for a period of 12 months.\r\nWhen there is work in your area, you will be sent an email message. If you accept the assignment, you are then able to enter the rest of our website and get your assignment. Follow the link to start the online application:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/shoppers_joinup.asp\">http://www.mysteryshopper.com.au/shoppers_joinup.asp</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Mystery Shopper website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nMystery Shoppers are independent contractors who receive rewards in the form of gift vouchers, or bank deposits. In addition, on many assignments, free goods and/or services are also available. The amount you will get paid varies by the type of assignment you complete. Payments generally range between $15 to $80 per assignment.','no'),(2472,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2473,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_exclusion','','no'),(2474,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2475,'options_compatibility_check_providers_55_country','AU','no'),(2476,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_55_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2477,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_logo','483','no'),(2478,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2479,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_name','Love Home Swap','no'),(2480,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2481,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_Website','www.lovehomeswap.com','no'),(2482,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2483,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_potential',' free holiday accommodation','no'),(2484,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2485,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nHave you ever thought about home swapping for holiday or for longer? Here is your experience solution, it\'s called Love Home Swap. They have the best choice with thousands of unique homes all over the world.\r\nThey make it quick and easy. Their online calendar lets you discover instantly if the home you want is available. We have no limits. All their members can swap homes as often as they want.\r\nThere are over 700,000 member opinions on their website, plus their helpful customer team is always on hand. We give you exclusive travel benefits, from airport lounge passes to local guides and 5* concierge It\'s a paid subscription, you have 3 options of membership to choose. You also have a free trial.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Love Home Swap:\r\n\r\nYou need a place a home or apartment that you can swap. It\'s as simple as messaging other members and taking it from there. You\'ll have two choices when you swap:\r\nDirect swap\r\nYou go to theirs. They come to yours. Either swap homes at the same time or agree to stay on separate dates that don\'t coincide.\r\nPoints\r\nTheir clever Swap Points let you stay in other members\' homes without doing a direct swap (and vice versa).\r\n\r\nYou will need to choose your paid membership plan.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/how-it-works\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/choose\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/choose</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/faqs\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/faqs</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/terms-and-conditions\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/terms-and-conditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/privacy-policy\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Love Home Swap on hello@lovehomeswap.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Love Home Swap\r\n\r\nYou have an option of a free trial, to start your free option, follow the link below to register:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.lovehomeswap.com/details\">https://www.lovehomeswap.com/details</a>\r\n\r\nOnce your free trial is over, you have 3 options of membership to choose from.\r\n\r\nSimply sign up with a few basic details, then search for a home by telling them when and where you\'d like to travel. Click \'Contact member\' on the property that you want to rent, to send the owner an enquiry.\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Love Home Swap website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou earn the free holiday accommodation that can cost you a few hundreds of a couple of thousands of dollars if you are in a prime location. Cancellation police fees apply, Love Home Swap commission fees apply.','no'),(2486,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2487,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_exclusion','','no'),(2488,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2489,'options_compatibility_check_providers_56_country','AU','no'),(2490,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_56_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2491,'options_compatibility_check_providers_57_logo','485','no'),(2492,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_57_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2493,'options_compatibility_check_providers_57_name','Skillshare ','no'),(2494,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_57_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2495,'options_compatibility_check_providers_57_Website','www.skillshare.com','no'),(2496,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_57_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2497,'options_compatibility_check_providers_57_potential','from $200 a month ','no'),(2498,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_57_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2499,'options_compatibility_check_providers_57_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nSkillshare is an online learning community with thousands of classes in design, business, teach, and more. Anyone can join the millions of members in the community to learn cutting-edge skills, network with peers, and discover new opportunities. You can become a teacher and get paid to do it. Their purpose is to make the new economy an open meritocracy, where the skills and expertise needed to succeed are available for anyone willing to learn them.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Skillshare:\r\n\r\nAnyone can teach a class. As long as your class adheres to their Publishing Guidelines, it can be published on Skillshare.\r\nThe Guidelines outlined for becoming a teacher is:\r\nFoster learning for the sake of learning.\r\nInclude a class project and meet their minimum standards for length and quality. (10 minutes per class minimum)\r\nAdhere to their Community Guidelines.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.skillshare.com/hc/en-us\">https://help.skillshare.com/hc/en-us</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://help.skillshare.com/hc/en-us/articles/204536438-Community-Guidelines\">https://help.skillshare.com/hc/en-us/articles/204536438-Community-Guidelines</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.skillshare.com/teach\">https://www.skillshare.com/teach</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.skillshare.com/teach/handbook/teaching-overview/204543318\">https://www.skillshare.com/teach/handbook/teaching-overview/204543318</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.skillshare.com/terms\">https://www.skillshare.com/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.skillshare.com/privacy\">https://www.skillshare.com/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Skillshare on teach@skillshare.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Skillshare:\r\n\r\nTo start, click sign up located at the top right corner of the website, fill an online form and create your profile. Once all done then follow the process of creating your first class.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.skillshare.com/\">www.skillshare.com</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Skillshare website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nTeachers on Skillshare earn revenue through royalty payments and premium referrals.\r\nOn average, first-time teachers earn $200 in their first month on Skillshare, with top teachers earning upwards of $3,000!\r\n\r\nFollow the link below for more information:\r\n<a href=\"https