s/how-it-works?c=AUD</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://intercom.help/eatwith/faq-english\">https://intercom.help/eatwith/faq-english</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eatwith.com/landings/private-events?c=AUD\">https://www.eatwith.com/landings/private-events?c=AUD</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://intercom.help/eatwith/terms-and-conditions\">https://intercom.help/eatwith/terms-and-conditions</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://intercom.help/eatwith/terms-and-conditions/privacy-policy\">https://intercom.help/eatwith/terms-and-conditions/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Eatwith via email: support@eatwith.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Eatwith:\r\n\r\nClick on \'become a host\' and start your profile. You can sign up using your Facebook account or select sign up with email and fill in your full name, email address, and password in the form provided. Creating an account is totally free, whether youre looking to dine or host! After you sign up, make sure to fill out all your profile information before booking, so your hosts and fellow guests can get to know you better even before the event starts. Follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eatwith.com/accounts/sign-up?c=AUD&amp;redirect=%2Fdashboard%2Fmy-meals%2Fcreate\">https://www.eatwith.com/accounts/sign-up?c=AUD&amp;redirect=%2Fdashboard%2Fmy-meals%2Fcreate</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Eatwith website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYou set the price for your dining experience and the number of people that can attend.\r\nIf you invited 6 people, each person pays $100 for a 3-4 course dinner and you earn $600 (minus grocery shopping). For more information aboutEatwith commissions fees, please read terms and conditions.','no'),(2546,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_60_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2547,'options_compatibility_check_providers_60_exclusion','','no'),(2548,'_options_compatibility_check_