 links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/help/141/how-does-starnow-work\">https://www.starnow.com.au/help/141/how-does-starnow-work</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/help/142/who-can-join-starnow\">https://www.starnow.com.au/help/142/who-can-join-starnow</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/terms-and-conditions/\">https://www.starnow.com.au/terms-and-conditions/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/privacy-policy/\">https://www.starnow.com.au/privacy-policy/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/help/12/online-audition-safety-tips/\">https://www.starnow.com.au/help/12/online-audition-safety-tips/</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact StarNow via email: contact@starnow.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with StarNow:\r\n\r\nIt\'s free to create a Trial Membership which allows you to create a basic talent profile and apply to a limited number of jobs.\r\nTo appear in their Talent Directory and apply for unlimited jobs and auditions, you\'ll need to upgrade to one of their paid membership options which are about the cost of a fancy coffee a month.\r\nTo start your trial membership follow the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.starnow.com.au/register/?return_url=%2f\">https://www.starnow.com.au/register/?return_url=%2f</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the StarNow website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYour job searches on StarNow can be filtered by paid &amp; expenses, paid only, and expenses only. You choose if you are applying for a volunteer job with paid expenses or a paid job. Earnings vary per each individual job, you can earn a few hundred dollars per job or even per day and more if the job is paid.','no'),(2560,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_61_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2561,'options_compatibility_check_providers_61_exclusion','','no'),(2562,'_