 up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.oneflare.com.au/about\">https://www.oneflare.com.au/about</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://help.oneflare.com.au/hc/en-us\">https://help.oneflare.com.au/hc/en-us</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.oneflare.com.au/terms\">https://www.oneflare.com.au/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.oneflare.com.au/privacy\">https://www.oneflare.com.au/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Oneflare on 13 18 18 or support@oneflare.com.au<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Oneflare:\r\n\r\nFill out the registration form in three simple steps.\r\nFollow the link below to get started:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.oneflare.com.au/businesses/new\">https://www.oneflare.com.au/businesses/new</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Oneflare website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nThere is a couple of different earning potential. You can earn anything from$20 to $100 per service and much more. To understand how to make most out of them and how to provide effective quotes, please read the information on the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.oneflare.com.au/hc/en-us/articles/215560428-Send-a-quote\">https://help.oneflare.com.au/hc/en-us/articles/215560428-Send-a-quote</a>','no'),(2574,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_62_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2575,'options_compatibility_check_providers_62_exclusion','','no'),(2576,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_62_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2577,'options_compatibility_check_providers_62_country','AU','no'),(2578,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_62_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2579,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_logo','503','no'),(2580,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2581,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_name','Zibbet','no'),(2582,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2583,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_Website','www.zibbet.com','no'),(2584,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2585,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_potential','from $1 to a few hundred a month','no'),(2586,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2587,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nZibbet is a marketplace powered by a global community of independent artists, crafters, and vintage collectors. It\'s a place where you can buy the most amazing, unique, and inspiring products that can\'t be found anywhere else. Zibbet is a platform that helps creative entrepreneurs sell more of their products. You can build your very own stand-alone website/ shop with Zibbet, that is fully customizable and easy to build without any technical skills, its DYI.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Zibbet:\r\n\r\nProducts in the Handmade and Fine Art categories must be handmade by the individual/s running the Zibbet store. Hand-assembled and Hand-altered items are also acceptable.\r\nIt\'s important to note that mass-produced products are not allowed on Zibbet in the Handmade and Fine Art categories, even if they are handmade.\r\nWhen you sell on Zibbet, you can enjoy the freedom of not paying any listing fees for each product you list. Zibbet doesn\'t charge a commission fee on your sales either, so you get to keep your profits.\r\nZibbet\'s fees work on a subscription model. Its free up to 10 listings (10 products) and then you have 3 plans to chose from $5, $10, $20 a month subscription fees.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zibbet.com/about-us\">https://www.zibbet.com/about-us</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zibbet.com/sell\">https://www.zibbet.com/sell</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://support.zibbet.com/\">http://support.zibbet.com/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zibbet.com/terms-of-use\">https://www.zibbet.com/terms-of-use</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zibbet.com/privacy-policy\">https://www.zibbet.com/privacy-policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Zibbet via email: support@zibbet.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Zibbet:\r\n\r\nRegister your free account, follow the link below to start:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.zibbet.com/sell/sign-up/free\">https://www.zibbet.com/sell/sign-up/free</a>\r\n\r\nOnce you register, start creating the \"storefront.\" For instructions follow the link below:\r\n<a href=\"http://support.zibbet.com/customizing-your-zibbet-website-and-marketplace-store\">http://support.zibbet.com/customizing-your-zibbet-website-and-marketplace-store</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Zibbet website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYour earnings potential will depend on your marketability, volume of sales, and how much each of your products costs. It can be anything from $1 to a few hundred or thousands a month.','no'),(2588,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2589,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_exclusion','','no'),(2590,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2591,'options_compatibility_check_providers_63_country','AU','no'),(2592,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_63_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2593,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_logo','508','no'),(2594,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2595,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_name','ArtFire','no'),(2596,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2597,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_Website','www.artfire.com','no'),(2598,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2599,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_potential','from $1 to a few hundred a month','no'),(2600,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2601,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nArtFire is a marketplace, craft, and maker, a community where people from around the world come together to buy, sell, and interact.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Artfire:\r\n\r\nYou can sell handmade goods, vintage items, and craft supplies on ArtFire. You have to open an account, enter the paid subscription option and open the shop with ArtFire to join their community.\r\nSelect the plan that\'s right for you with no long-term commitment. Change your plan any time you want.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.artfire.com/ext/pages/craftsy\">https://www.artfire.com/ext/pages/craftsy</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.artfire.com/ext/help/page/faq\">https://www.artfire.com/ext/help/page/faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.artfire.com/ext/help/page/TOU\">https://www.artfire.com/ext/help/page/TOU</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.artfire.com/modules.php?name=privacy_policy\">https://www.artfire.com/modules.php?name=privacy_policy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact ArtFire via email: service@artfire.com\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with ArtFire:\r\n\r\nArtFire offers 3 types of seller accounts: a Standard/Per Item plan; A Popular Shop plan and; a Featured Shop plan.\r\nTo join the community of talented artisans, click on the \'Start Today\' link (see link below). You\'ll be walked through the process of setting up an account, and you\'ll see the account options that are currently available. Remember, your username will be your shop name and cannot duplicate another shop name on the site. Your username may not have spaces or non-alphanumeric characters, as this will cause the URL for your shop to break.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.artfire.com/ext/sell/start_today\">https://www.artfire.com/ext/sell/start_today</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Artfire website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYour earnings potential will depend on your marketability, volume of sales, and how much each of your products costs. It can be anything from $1 to a few hundred or thousands a month.','no'),(2602,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2603,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_exclusion','','no'),(2604,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2605,'options_compatibility_check_providers_64_country','AU','no'),(2606,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_64_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2607,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_logo','511','no'),(2608,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2609,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_name','Dishme','no'),(2610,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2611,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_Website','www.dishme.com.au','no'),(2612,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2613,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_potential','from $100 to $1000 or more','no'),(2614,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2615,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nDishme is a food delivery service where amautuer and professional chefs can sign up and get paid to cook buffets for paying customers. It\'s like you getting a personal cook on demand. If you are a fantastic home cook, amateur chef, or a professional chef, a world of opportunities awaits you! Dishme currently operates in Sydney only, watch for rollout to your cities.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Dishme:\r\n\r\nAbility to cook tasty food.\r\nYou work from the comfort of your kitchen and cook what you are the best at. You need to get your menu approved by Dishme. Once set up, start receiving orders (based on your availability) to cook and deliver nearby. They will help you create a buffet (from your dishes) and that is what customers order from.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/whyusedishme\">https://www.dishme.com.au/whyusedishme</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/applytocook\">https://www.dishme.com.au/applytocook</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/faq/cook\">https://www.dishme.com.au/faq/cook</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/support/terms\">https://www.dishme.com.au/support/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/support/privacy\">https://www.dishme.com.au/support/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Dishme via email: support@dishme.com.au\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Dishme:\r\n\r\nSimply register and create your online profile. Once completed, they will call you within 48 hours.\r\nMeet-up with their community manager and learn how to be an efficient cook.\r\nFire up the oven, heat up the pans, put on your apron, and start making money.\r\n\r\nfollow the link below to register:\r\n<a href=\"https://www.dishme.com.au/auth/apply\">https://www.dishme.com.au/auth/apply</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Dishme website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nYour earning is based on how many orders you complete. Earnings per order may vary from $100 to $1000, or more. Dishme takes a 20% fee on the total order amount and the rest is credited to your bank account in 3 days.','no'),(2616,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2617,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_exclusion','','no'),(2618,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2619,'options_compatibility_check_providers_65_country','AU','no'),(2620,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_65_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2621,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_logo','513','no'),(2622,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2623,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_name','Amazon','no'),(2624,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2625,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_Website','www.amazon.com.au','no'),(2626,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2627,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_potential','from $1 to a few hundred a month','no'),(2628,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2629,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nAmazon, is one of the biggest global marketplaces for buyers and sellers. You can join Amazon as a seller and sell new to lightly used products. The website is free to use for buyers, but sellers are charged fees for listing items.\r\n\r\n<strong>Minimum Requirements</strong>\r\n\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Amazon:\r\n\r\nMust have an ABN, Australian Bank account, and all products must follow the seller guidelines for each category they fall in, so rules differ from product to product. More than 20 categories are open for selling on the Amazon Marketplace in Australia. Only new products in these categories can be listed. Some categories have additional guidelines that sellers must follow, and some specific products within the categories have an approval requirement.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/how-it-works.html?ref=as_au_en_header_howitworks\">https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/how-it-works.html?ref=as_au_en_header_howitworks</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/eligible-categories.html?ref=as_au_en_header_categories\">https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/eligible-categories.html?ref=as_au_en_header_categories</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/pricing.html?ref=as_au_en_header_pricing\">https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/pricing.html?ref=as_au_en_header_pricing</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/faq.html?ref=as_au_en_snav_faq\">https://services.amazon.com.au/services/sell-on-amazon/faq.html?ref=as_au_en_snav_faq</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com.au/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=footer_cou?ie=UTF8&amp;nodeId=508088\">https://www.amazon.com.au/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=footer_cou?ie=UTF8&amp;nodeId=508088</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Amazon via the link below: <a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/contact-us.htm?ref=as_au_en_footer_cu\">https://services.amazon.com.au/contact-us.htm?ref=as_au_en_footer_cu</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Amazon:\r\n\r\nThe first step is to register, you will need an internationally chargeable credit card. You must be able to provide an Australian bank account to receive payment from Amazon.com.au. You may be required to supply documentation so that Amazon can verify your identity (Government issued ID and bank statement). This documentation needs to be in English (or a notarised English translation) or Chinese.\r\nBefore you begin the registration process, please make sure that you have the following information available:\r\nYour business name as you would like it to be displayed on Amazon.com.au\r\nThe name of the individual or entity that operates the business\r\nThe physical address of your business\r\nYour business credit card number and expiration date\r\nThe address where you receive your credit card statement\r\n\r\nTo start, click on Sign in to your Seller Account, this will give you the opportunity to register as a new user.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://services.amazon.com.au/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ld=AZAUSOA-sell\">https://services.amazon.com.au/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ld=AZAUSOA-sell</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Amazon website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nIn Amazon, you can earn per item, you set your own prices, you can earn anything from $1 to a couple of thousands a month and more.','no'),(2630,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2631,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_exclusion','','no'),(2632,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2633,'options_compatibility_check_providers_66_country','AU','no'),(2634,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_66_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2635,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_logo','516','no'),(2636,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2637,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_name','eBay','no'),(2638,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2639,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_Website','www.ebay.com.au','no'),(2640,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2641,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_potential','from $1 to a few hundred a month','no'),(2642,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2643,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\neBay is an online auction and marketplace website in which people and businesses buy and sell a wide variety of goods and services worldwide. The website is free to use for buyers, but sellers are charged fees for listing items after a limited number of free listings, and again, when those items are sold. In addition to its original auction-style sales, the website has since evolved and expanded to include \"Buy It Now\" shopping and other options.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with eBay:\r\n\r\nYou must own or have the products you are willing to sell. If you\'re a business, you must have an ABN. An Australian bank account or PayPal account is also needed. All products sold must be represented truthfully.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/\">https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/selling-fees\">https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/selling-fees</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/selling-on-ebay\">https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/selling-on-ebay</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.ebay.com.au/help/policies/selling-policies/selling-practices-policy?id=4346#section2\">https://www.ebay.com.au/help/policies/selling-policies/selling-practices-policy?id=4346#section2</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.ebay.com.au/help/selling/selling/selling?id=4081#seller-basics\">https://www.ebay.com.au/help/selling/selling/selling?id=4081#seller-basics</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.ebay.com.au/help/policies/member-behaviour-policies/user-agreement?id=4259\">https://www.ebay.com.au/help/policies/member-behaviour-policies/user-agreement?id=4259</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact eBay on 1800 322 928.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with eBay:\r\n\r\nYoull need a seller account. Setting up your account is free and only takes a few minutes. The type of account you need will depend on if you are a casual seller or a business seller. You can choose between a personal or business account. If you plan to sell casually, like selling items you no longer need or want, a personal account is the best option. Pick a business account if you want to sell large quantities, or have items that you\'ve made or bought to resell.\r\n\r\nFollow the link below to find out more and to choose right account: <a href=\"https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/content/set-your-selling-account\">https://sellercentre.ebay.com.au/content/set-your-selling-account</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the eBay website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nIt depends on the products you are selling and the demand for the product. There are selling limits depending on your account and customer satisfaction. You can earn anything from $1 to a couple of thousands a month and more.','no'),(2644,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2645,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_exclusion','','no'),(2646,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2647,'options_compatibility_check_providers_67_country','AU','no'),(2648,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_67_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2649,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_logo','518','no'),(2650,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2651,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_name','Handkrafted','no'),(2652,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2653,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_Website','www.handkrafted.com','no'),(2654,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2655,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_potential','from $1 to a few hundred a month','no'),(2656,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2657,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nHandkrafted works by crowdsourcing makers who create a variety of bespoke products and then matching them with customers. Makers send tailored proposals in response to briefs posted by customers, who can then choose which maker they would like to commission.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Handkrafted:\r\n\r\nThey have an initial focus on woodworkers and custom furniture makers, they are currently expanding to metalworkers, lighting makers, upholsterers, and concrete artisans. They will continue expanding available crafts over time, so keep watching it for your craft skills if they not there yet.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all the requirements and conditions before applying.<strong></strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.handkrafted.com/hc/en-us/categories/200194570-For-Makers\">https://help.handkrafted.com/hc/en-us/categories/200194570-For-Makers</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/how-it-works\">https://www.handkrafted.com/how-it-works</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/why-handkrafted\">https://www.handkrafted.com/why-handkrafted</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/design-professionals\">https://www.handkrafted.com/design-professionals</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://help.handkrafted.com/hc/en-us\">https://help.handkrafted.com/hc/en-us</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/terms\">https://www.handkrafted.com/terms</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/privacy\">https://www.handkrafted.com/privacy</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Handkrafted via email: info@handkrafted.com or +61 (0) 412 113371\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Handkrafted:\r\n\r\nHandkrafted asks interested makers to complete a basic application form to help them assess your style of work and preferences. Its important to reference any examples of your prior work (for example, via your website, Facebook page, Instagram account, or photos etc..) follow the link below to register:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.handkrafted.com/register\">https://www.handkrafted.com/register</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Handkrafted website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nHow much you can earn will depend on many factors, on the hours you are willing to put in for building the furniture or woodwork as well as the material you are going to use. You can earn from a few dollars to a few hundredor thousands. For guidance, here are six of the key variables influencing the cost of having a piece of furniture custom made, see link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://blog.handkrafted.com/factors-influencing-the-cost-of-custom-furniture/\">https://blog.handkrafted.com/factors-influencing-the-cost-of-custom-furniture/</a>','no'),(2658,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2659,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_exclusion','','no'),(2660,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2661,'options_compatibility_check_providers_68_country','AU','no'),(2662,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_68_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2663,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_logo','522','no'),(2664,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_logo','field_5ba360ff8b5f7','no'),(2665,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_name','Etsy ','no'),(2666,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_name','field_5ba360ff8b5f8','no'),(2667,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_Website','www.etsy.com','no'),(2668,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_Website','field_5ba360ff8b5f9','no'),(2669,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_potential','from $10 to a few thousand per item','no'),(2670,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_potential','field_5ba360ff8b5fa','no'),(2671,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_description','<h4><strong>How it works</strong></h4>\r\nEtsy is a website where you can post and sell vintage and handmade items. If you are talented in handcraft items, you can open your Etsy shop and start selling and earning.\r\n<h4><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h4>\r\nHeres the minimum requirement to start working with Etsy:\r\n\r\nYou need an ABN and Items that meet the criteria of being 30 years or older and are handmade.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure you read all requirements and conditions before applying\r\n<h4><strong>Useful information\'s to review and comply with before you start</strong><strong></strong></h4>\r\nHere are the useful links with the information to know and review before you sign up:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/au/about?ref=ftr\">https://www.etsy.com/au/about?ref=ftr</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://help.etsy.com/hc/en-us\">https://help.etsy.com/hc/en-us</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/au/legal/?ref=ftr\">https://www.etsy.com/au/legal/?ref=ftr</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/au/legal/privacy/?ref=ftr\">https://www.etsy.com/au/legal/privacy/?ref=ftr</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Etsy via one of the options on the link below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://help.etsy.com/hc/en-us/articles/115013375488-Contacting-Us\">https://help.etsy.com/hc/en-us/articles/115013375488-Contacting-Us</a>\r\n<h4><strong>How to start</strong></h4>\r\nTo start with Etsy:\r\n\r\nFollow these steps:\r\nStep 1: Review Etsy\'s Terms of Use and Privacy Policy\r\nStep 2: \'Click Register\' at the top of the site\r\nStep 3: Fill out the form\r\nStep 4: Check your email and click to confirm\r\nStep 5: Sign in to Etsy\r\n\r\nYou need anEtsy account first, and then you can begin to list items that meet their criteria and start earning.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/\">https://www.etsy.com/</a>\r\n\r\nPlease read all terms and conditions on the Etsy website before starting.\r\n<h4><strong>How much you can earn</strong></h4>\r\nDepending on items and the price you set, you can make from $10 per item up to a few thousand per month or year.','no'),(2672,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_description','field_5ba360ff8b5fb','no'),(2673,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_exclusion','','no'),(2674,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_exclusion','field_5ba3710b13fdf','no'),(2675,'options_compatibility_check_providers_69_country','AU','no'),(2676,'_options_compatibility_check_providers_69_country','field_5ba370e913fde','no'),(2677,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_58.173.113.66','1538291808','no'),(2678,'_transient_external_ip_address_58.173.113.66','111.67.5.164','no'),(2679,'_transient_timeout_external_ip_address_66.220.149.25','1538291840','no'),(2680,'_transient_external_ip_addres