rnal\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},{\"text\":\"<b>Professional expertise:<\\/b> We all have expertise in something that\\u2019s either work or interest-related, and we provide the opportunities to capitalise on them by sharing and advising.\",\"icon\":\"fa fa-check-circle\",\"_id\":\"41fdaa6\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},{\"text\":\"<b>Creativity and experience:<\\/b> You can share your passion and make money by doing what you love, sharing your creativity, designing unforgettable experiences, and sharing them either in your local community or online.\",\"icon\":\"fa fa-check-circle\",\"_id\":\"2f52bfc\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},{\"text\":\"<b>Home & space:<\\/b> Do you have a spare house, room, driveway, or any other space that can make you a little extra cash? There are endless opportunities using what you already have.\",\"icon\":\"fa fa-check-circle\",\"_id\":\"38656f4\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},{\"text\":\"<b>Wheels:<\\/b> Do you own something on wheels? Want to share it with others and get paid for doing so?\",\"icon\":\"fa fa-check-circle\",\"_id\":\"5d8313b\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},{\"text\":\"<b>Equipment & tools:<\\/b> Do you have any gadgets, tools, or toys that you can share? There are opportunities to share and earn those things you already have.\",\"icon\":\"fa fa-check-circle\",\"_id\":\"e50cafb\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}}],\"space_between\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16},\"icon_color\":\"#76cfa2\",\"icon_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":22},\"text_indent\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":11}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"icon-list\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"0aaa79b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a3c8c7c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"icon_list\":[{\"text\":\"<b>Time:<\\/b> Maybe y