tirees. It\\u2019s a place where experience meets opportunity. 4Retirees was created with one clear focus; to help retirees easily take advantage of a new world of opportunities. It\\u2019s a meeting place of ideas, inspiration, and experienced people. One of those opportunities is the online and on-demand economy that offers a new way to future-proof your retirement dreams. This new way of working lets you earn additional income while still maintaining the freedom to do the things you love most. No one knows better than a retiree how much the world can change in a lifetime. And 4Retirees is the network that helps you keep up with and benefit from those changes\\u2014all at a pace you\\u2019re comfortable with.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"fff4079\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Do I have to be tech-savvy to use 4Retirees?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>No. 4Retirees is run for retirees, by retirees. We\\u2019ve made it easy for you to get started. If you can read and tap on a keyboard, you can participate now and take our <a href=\\\"#FICC\\\"><strong>Free Compatibility Check<\\/strong><\\/a>. And, when you\\u2019re ready to learn some new technology skills, we\\u2019ll be there too. Our aim is to help you to keep pace with this burgeoning economy and part of that is upskilling your technology skills. These improved skills will help you to unlock a future filled with more opportunities for earning income, taking advantage of tools available to you, so that you can live your dream retirement life and keep you better connected to your friends, family, and the rest of the world.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"7412f4e\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Who participates in 4Retirees community?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Anyone who is chasing a dream of freedom is participating in the 4Retirees community. Anyone who is thinking of career change to enable their potential and opportunities can participate in our community and take advantage of what\\u2019s on offer. If you have an interest in the on-demand economy, we invite you to start your journey here by taking our <a href=\\\"#FICC\\\"><strong>Free Compatibility Check.<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"80a5f07\"},{\"tab_title\":\"In what ways will I be able to connect with other retirees?  \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Our vision is to build a better place for all retirees. Our big goal at first is to bring you all together and to establish the connections. We know that people do business and learn from people they know, like, and trust. So, first things first, we\\u2019ll concentrate on providing opportunities to come together so we can all benefit the advantage of the technology and the on-demand economy. We want to create a community of retirees4retirees, eventually we can co-create, build a better place with a better economy where all retirees come to connect, interact, meet, help each other, share their skills, build new ones, volunteer, earn money, and maybe even make some friends! We will provide you soon with opportunities to participate in forums, to connect, chat, share ideas, and ask questions about your fellow community members. You can also connect with the community through most of our social media channels. Make sure to sign up for our eNewsletter so we keep you up to date on our progress as our community grows and becomes an even \\u201cbetter place for retirees.\\u201d<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"be0573c\"},{\"tab_title\":\"How do I manage my subscription preferences?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Once you take our <a href=\\\"#FICC\\\"><strong>Free Compatibility Check<\\/strong><\\/a> or sign up to our eNewsletter, we will create an account for you and send you link to activate via email. You can manage your preferences by accessing right top corner of your account under the button that says \'<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/4retirees.com\\/my-account\\\" data-wplink-url-error=\\\"true\\\">Login<\\/a>\' or \\u2018<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/4retirees.com\\/my-account\\\" data-wplink-url-error=\\\"true\\\">My account<\\/a>\\u201d. If you would like to receive our weekly eNewsletter with useful tips and hints, or perhaps you would like to update your interest information so that we can provide you with more comprehensive updates weekly, you can do all of that in through your account preferences.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"83a6fbd\"},{\"tab_title\":\"I forgot my password, how do I reset it?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>You can manage this under your account - right top corner - you can request a password reset, or before you login, reset by clicking on \\u2018<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/4retirees.com\\/wp-login.php?action=lostpassword\\\" data-wplink-url-error=\\\"true\\\">forgot my password<\\/a>.\\u2019<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"f199d98\"},{\"tab_title\":\"How do I deactivate my account? \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>We would certainly be sorry to see you go, but if you really want to, you can simply unsubscribe from all the communication or you can deactivate your account. You can manage these preferences under the \\u201c<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/4retirees.com\\/my-account\\\" data-wplink-url-error=\\\"true\\\">My Account<\\/a>\\u201d tab located in the right top corner, through the button, \\u201cDeactivate Account.\\u201d<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"5c5f6ac\"}],\"icon\":\"fa fa-question-circle-o\",\"icon_active\":\"fa fa-question-circle\",\"border_color\":\"#c8cbdd\",\"title_color\":\"#5c6181\",\"tab_active_color\":\"#313551\",\"title_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"20\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":true},\"title_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true},\"icon_color\":\"#5c6181\",\"icon_active_color\":\"#f57515\",\"content_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"30\",\"bottom\":\"10\",\"left\":\"50\",\"isLinked\":false},\"content_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"18\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"18\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"accordion\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"500bcf5\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":704},\"border_border\":\"solid\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"1\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"1\",\"isLinked\":false},\"border_color\":\"#c8cbdd\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"25\",\"right\":\"20\",\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e62438c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null,\"space_between_widgets\":0,\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"10\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"10\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8b0b9f5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>If we didn\'t answer your question or you need additional clarification, email us at <a href=\\\"mailto:faq@4retirees.com\\\">faq@4retirees.com<\\/a> and we will respond to you just as quickly as we can!<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#5c6181\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_style\":\"italic\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"dc2bd28\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"gap\":\"extended\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"60\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9e289fa\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a79199b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"gap\":\"no\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"border_color\":\"#c8cbdd\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3351549\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"87a0491\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Learn all about on-demand economy\",\"title_color\":\"#f57515\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_border_border\":\"solid\",\"_border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_border_color\":\"#c8cbdd\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"022e28b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"gap\":\"no\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b45561a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null,\"space_between_widgets\":0},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bcd5fc2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tabs\":[{\"tab_title\":\"What exactly is the on-demand economy?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>The on-demand economy is defined as the economic activity created by technology companies that fulfil consumer demand via the immediate provisioning of goods and services. The on-demand economy, also known as a sharing economy or collaborative consumption or the peer economy, is a trending business concept that highlights the ability (and perhaps the preference) of individuals to rent or borrow goods or services and not necessarily buy and own them. Owners rent out something they are not using, such as a car, house, bicycle, or their skills, to someone else using these peer-to-peer services and earning money on demand.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"fff4079\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Can you give me some examples of businesses in the on-demand economy? \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>We have a comprehensive list of over hundreds of on-demand economy businesses right here in Australia. Two that you have most likely heard of are UBER and Airbnb. With UBER, people use their own cars, sign up as drivers, and then transport people or deliver food to other people as part of their peer-to-peer network. You can work on your terms, the hours you want, in the area you want, and still earn money while meeting new people and listening to your favourite radio station. The second example is Airbnb. It is an online marketplace and hospitality service for people to lease or rent short-term lodging including holiday cottages, rooms, apartments, homestays, hostel beds, etc. You can do this all year long if you have a place you never use, for weeks at a time when you are travelling, or just until you find new tenants for your investment property.\\u00a0 It\\u2019s a great contemporary (and cheaper) alternative to hotel accommodation. We can match you with hundreds of these types of businesses\\u2014the choice of businesses participating in the on-demand economy is virtually endless and new ones are popping up all the time. You\\u2019ll be able to find transportation, hobby-related businesses, travel, education, business services, delivery, pet care, and the works!<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"7412f4e\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Why is the on-demand economy growing so fast?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>The <strong>on-demand economy <\\/strong>is here to stay. And its growth is a given.\\u00a0 Whether it\\u2019s renting a room, hiring a driver, renting a parking space, or outsourcing household tasks, the sharing economy is disrupting a range of industries and causing regulators to take note. Technology is making it easier for new marketplaces to be created. Services that used to be high touch, slow to deliver, but yet expensive are now fast and efficient, thanks to technology like smart phones. This creates a better experience for the consumer and also the person providing the service. Australia has a supportive start-up community with new businesses starting up all the time, and we are here to provide you with this comprehensive research in discovering new options for earning an income all the time. It\\u2019s an incredibly exciting time!<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"80a5f07\"},{\"tab_title\":\"How can I start earning money in the on-demand economy? \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>The first step is to understand your compatibility with the opportunities available. Take our <a href=\\\"#FICC\\\"><strong>Free Compatibility Check<\\/strong><\\/a> and see if your current circumstances match any of these on-demand businesses and how much you could potentially earn. Once you receive your results, then you decide if it makes sense for you to purchase access to your custom <strong>On-Demand Opportunities List <\\/strong>so that you can then pursue your matching income-generating opportunities.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"be0573c\"},{\"tab_title\":\"How much I can get paid from the on-demand economy? \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Once you buy your personalised and comprehensive <strong>On-Demand Opportunities List<\\/strong>, you can explore each individual opportunity you matched with, sign up to do it, start working, and start earning from your very first day. In the on-demand economy, you have the potential to earn per hour, per day, per week, or per item or project. It\\u2019s possible to earn anywhere from $20 per hour to thousands of dollars\\u2014or more\\u2014per week or per month. Your earning potential depends on your skill set, situation, the opportunities available, and how little or how much you\\u2019re prepared to do. The choice is yours! And, you\\u2019re not locked into committing to any time frames. You can dip in or out when it makes sense for you.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"83a6fbd\"},{\"tab_title\":\"How do I get paid from these individual on-demand economy businesses?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Each of these businesses have their own individual payment systems and conditions that you should review before signing up. Payment is usually made directly to your bank account or PayPal account. Fast payment is one of the benefits of the on-demand economy. After you have provided a service via one of the on-demand economy businesses, some payments are received within 1-3 business days, others or on a designated day each week or month. We definitely recommend that you to check this with each business before you start. And, we recommend speaking with your accountant or tax\\/financial adviser about your individual circumstances.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"f199d98\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Is the on-demand economy legal?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>The on-demand economy and participation in it is most definitely legal and it is even supported by Australian Government. You, as a participant in it, are fully supported by Australian Consumer Law while using the on-demand sharing economy. To find out more, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/consumerlaw.gov.au\\/business-and-the-acl\\/sharing-economy-platforms\\/\\\">CLICK HERE<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"5c5f6ac\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Do I pay TAX or\\/and GST when earning on-demand economy? \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>The Australian Government is fully supportive of participation in the on-demand economy and has introduced a number of protection laws for consumers, including taxation and GST. In general, just like other sources of employment, the on-demand economy is subject to taxation and GST. The Australian Tax Office has some helpful information about tax and the on-demand economy GST, to find out more, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ato.gov.au\\/general\\/the-sharing-economy-and-tax\\/income-tax-and-GST-in-the-sharing-economy\\/\\\">CLICK HERE<\\/a>. If you need more information, we then recommend you to contact your accountant or tax\\/financial adviser to assess your personal circumstances.<\\/p><p>If we didn\'t answer your question or you need additional clarification, email us at <a href=\\\"mailto:faq@4retirees.com\\\">faq@4retirees.com<\\/a> and we will respond to you just as quickly as we can!<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"b2d4122\"}],\"icon\":\"fa fa-question-circle-o\",\"icon_active\":\"fa fa-question-circle\",\"border_color\":\"#c8cbdd\",\"title_color\":\"#5c6181\",\"tab_active_color\":\"#313551\",\"title_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"20\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":true},\"title_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"