Better yet, it also gives you new opportunities to improve your current situation and reward yourself. Again, all on your own terms.</p><p>How can you get connected to on-demand opportunities? Start by taking the<strong> 4Retirees Income Compatibility Check</strong></p>		\n										<img width=\"600\" height=\"455\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-on-demand-economy.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-on-demand-economy.jpg 600w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-on-demand-economy-150x114.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-on-demand-economy-300x228.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" />											\n										<img width=\"545\" height=\"362\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-Free-Income-Compatibility-Check-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-Free-Income-Compatibility-Check-1.jpg 545w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-Free-Income-Compatibility-Check-1-150x100.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-Free-Income-Compatibility-Check-1-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" />											\n		<h3>What is the Free Income Compatibility Check? </h3><p>Our compatibility check is designed to match your personal circumstances with the opportunities that are most relevant to you, all in real time. We have designed a short checklist to better understand your current personal and economic situation, e.g Do you own a car? Do you like helping others? etc. This short Free Income Compatibility Check takes just a minute to complete, and it can identify all sorts of opportunities for you.</p><h3>How does it work?</h3><p>We have developed an online digital matching tool that asks you 14 short questions and then utilises a rating and matching system to present you with opportunities suitable to your circumstance. We match you with available on-demand economy opportunities in real time in just three simple steps.</p>		\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/How-does-it-work.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/How-does-it-work.jpg 560w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/How-does-it-work-150x140.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/How-does-it-work-300x281.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n										<img width=\"190\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-1-Answer-some-questions.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-1-Answer-some-questions.png 190w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-1-Answer-some-questions-150x142.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 190px) 100vw, 190px\" />											\n		<h4>Answer some questions</h4>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Answer 14 short questions in our <b>Free Income Compatibility Check.</b>\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We will analyse your answers and generate results automatically in real time.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										It takes just a minute to complete. \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"191\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results.png 191w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results-150x141.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 191px) 100vw, 191px\" />											\n		<h4>Get your results</h4>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Free results will be send to you via email in real time.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										The results are based on your answers and will provide you with a number of on-demand economy businesses you have matched with and the potential <b>estimated earnings</b> value per month.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"191\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning.png 191w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning-150x141.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 191px) 100vw, 191px\" />											\n		<h4>Start earning</h4>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Once you recieve your free results and you are happy with a number of businesses you matched with, then purchase personalised to your circumstances <b>On-Demand Opportunity List</b>, sign up with those businesses and start earning. \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We suggest using the common sense and good judgement that got you this far.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"440\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1.jpg 560w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1-150x118.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1-300x236.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n		<h3>What is the On-Demand Opportunities List?</h3><p>It is a personalised to your circumstances list of all the businesses you have matched with, you can get the list with one-off payment. The list will contain business name, conditions of participation, terms of use, how to start, how much you can earn from each individual business. All the necessary information you need to start earning are in one place created for you in your member account, researched and updated weekly so that you keep getting more continually. The faster you sign up and work, the faster you can start earning.</p><h3>7 reasons to join 4Retirees</h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Its Australias No1 online compatibility matcher with on-demand income opportunities.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Free Income Compatibility Check that estimates the number of opportunity matches for you, and their potential earning values in real time.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										All the necessary information you need to start earning from day 1 are in one place in your member account, researched and updated continually so that you keep getting more.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Flexible arrangements are forged on your terms.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Transparent disclosure of all commercial relationships.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Opportunities to participate in your local area, meet neighbours, and help build a stronger and more connected community.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										A chance to earn additional income, reward yourself, make connections, and improve your lifestyleliving more on your own terms.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<h3>What type of on-demand economy businesses does 4Retirees support? </h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										We support businesses that have a clear mission and are built on meaningful and worthwhile principles, including transparency, humanness, and authenticity that all influence strategic decisions in both the short and long terms.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We back businesses that are providers on the supply-side are valued, respected, and empowered, committed companies that make the lives of these providers economically and socially better.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We support the businesses that help customers on the demand side of the platforms who should benefit from the ability to get goods and services in more efficient and effective way.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We back businesses that are built on distributed marketplaces or decentralized networks that create a sense of community and belonging, collective accountability, and mutual benefit.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<h3>What kind of on-demand opportunities will you find with 4Retirees?</h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										<b>Online and on-demand:</b> We use online websites and apps that allow you to share services, talents, or goods.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Professional expertise:</b> We all have expertise in something thats either work or interest-related, and we provide the opportunities to capitalise on them by sharing and advising.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Creativity and experience:</b> You can share your passion and make money by doing what you love, sharing your creativity, designing unforgettable experiences, and sharing them either in your local community or online.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Home & space:</b> Do you have a spare house, room, driveway, or any other space that can make you a little extra cash? There are endless opportunities using what you already have.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Wheels:</b> Do you own something on wheels? Want to share it with others and get paid for doing so?\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Equipment & tools:</b> Do you have any gadgets, tools, or toys that you can share? There are opportunities to share and earn those things you already have.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										<b>Time:</b> Maybe you have a few spare hours each day or weektime is money and is always on-demand.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Caring:</b> Are you a carer at heart? Maybe you love to help people or animals. There are heaps of opportunities to earn through caring.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Skill sharing:</b> Opportunities to share and teachwhether its juggling or giving a compelling presentation, there are financial opportunities in your special skills.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Amplifying your financial opportunities:</b> The availability of online marketplaces allows you to sell things or lend money to others and then be repaid with interest\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Stuff & such:</b> We all have plenty of stuff that we dont use, dont need, dont want, and wonder why we ever bought. Why not sell or rent it and turn it into some extra cash.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Choices in almost every category:</b> Business services, Delivery, Education, Family care, Health & beauty, Home services, Person-to-person (P2P) goods, Parking, Pet care, Reservations & ticketing, Shipping, Subscription, Transportation, and Travel.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<p>Still unsure or have more questions? </p><p>Please check our<a href=\"http://4retirees.com/support-centre/\" data-wplink-url-error=\"true\">Frequently Asked Questions</a></p>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2018-09-19 15:07:53','2018-09-19 05:37:53','',2,'http://4retirees.com/uncategorised/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(128,1,'2018-09-19 15:09:00','2018-09-19 05:39:00','<img src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Income-4-Retirees@2x-nwagfxvt9xrcrtjpqifr7lc6vazni2p6hqfojjorgg.png\" title=\"Income 4 Retirees@2x\" alt=\"Income 4 Retirees@2x\" />											\n		<p>Take adventures off hold, rediscover your life and start living those dreams. We are here to introduce you to the power of unlocking your earning potential no matter what your age or situation is, we want to make sure you keep reaping the rewards. </p>		\n			<a href=\"#more\" role=\"button\">\n						Discover more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"711\" height=\"408\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Matching-you-with-the-opportunities-you-deserve.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Matching-you-with-the-opportunities-you-deserve.jpg 711w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Matching-you-with-the-opportunities-you-deserve-150x86.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Matching-y