a minute to complete. \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"191\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results.png 191w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-2-Get-your-results-150x141.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 191px) 100vw, 191px\" />											\n		<h4>Get your results</h4>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Free results will be send to you via email in real time.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										The results are based on your answers and will provide you with a number of on-demand economy businesses you have matched with and the potential <b>estimated earnings</b> value per month.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"191\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning.png 191w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-3-Start-earning-150x141.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 191px) 100vw, 191px\" />											\n		<h4>Start earning</h4>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Once you recieve your free results and you are happy with a number of businesses you matched with, then purchase personalised to your circumstances <b>On-Demand Opportunity List</b>, sign up with those businesses and start earning. \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We suggest using the common sense and good judgement that got you this far.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"440\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1.jpg 560w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1-150x118.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/What-is-the-On-Demand-Opportunities-List-1-300x236.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n		<h3>What is the On-Demand Opportunities List?</h3><p>It is a personalised to your circumstances list of all the businesses you have matched with, you can get the list with one-off payment. The list will contain business name, conditions of participation, terms of use, how to start, how much you can earn from each individual business. All the necessary information you need to start earning are in one place created for you in your member account, researched and updated weekly so that you keep getting more continually. The faster you sign up and work, the faster you can start earning.</p><h3>7 reasons to join 4Retirees</h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Its Australias No1 online compatibility matcher with on-demand income opportunities.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Free Income Compatibility Check that estimates the number of opportunity matches for you, and their potential earning values in real time.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										All the necessary information you need to start earning from day 1 are in one place in your member account, researched and updated continually so that you keep getting more.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Flexible arrangements are forged on your terms.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Transparent disclosure of all commercial relationships.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Opportunities to participate in your local area, meet neighbours, and help build a stronger and more connected community.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										A chance to earn additional income, reward yourself, make connections, and improve your lifestyleliving more on your own terms.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<h3>What type of on-demand economy businesses does 4Retirees support? </h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										We support businesses that have a clear mission and are built on meaningful and worthwhile principles, including transparency, humanness, and authenticity that all influence strategic decisions in both the short and long terms.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We back businesses that are providers on the supply-side are valued, respected, and empowered, committed companies that make the lives of these providers economically and socially better.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We support the businesses that help customers on the demand side of the platforms who should benefit from the ability to get goods and services in more efficient and effective way.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										We back businesses that are built on distributed marketplaces or decentralized networks that create a sense of community and belonging, collective accountability, and mutual benefit.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<h3>What kind of on-demand opportunities will you find with 4Retirees?</h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										<b>Online and on-demand:</b> We use online websites and apps that allow you to share services, talents, or goods.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Professional expertise:</b> We all have expertise in something thats either work or interest-related, and we provide the opportunities to capitalise on them by sharing and advising.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Creativity and experience:</b> You can share your passion and make money by doing what you love, sharing your creativity, designing unforgettable experiences, and sharing them either in your local community or online.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Home & space:</b> Do you have a spare house, room, driveway, or any other space that can make you a little extra cash? There are endless opportunities using what you already have.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Wheels:</b> Do you own something on wheels? Want to share it with others and get paid for doing so?\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Equipment & tools:</b> Do you have any gadgets, tools, or toys that you can share? There are opportunities to share and earn those things you already have.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										<b>Time:</b> Maybe you have a few spare hours each day or weektime is money and is always on-demand.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Caring:</b> Are you a carer at heart? Maybe you love to help people or animals. There are heaps of opportunities to earn through caring.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Skill sharing:</b> Opportunities to share and teachwhether its juggling or giving a compelling presentation, there are financial opportunities in your special skills.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Amplifying your financial opportunities:</b> The availability of online marketplaces allows you to sell things or lend money to others and then be repaid with interest\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Stuff & such:</b> We all have plenty of stuff that we dont use, dont need, dont want, and wonder why we ever bought. Why not sell or rent it and turn it into some extra cash.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										<b>Choices in almost every category:</b> Business services, Delivery, Education, Family care, Health & beauty, Home services, Person-to-person (P2P) goods, Parking, Pet care, Reservations & ticketing, Shipping, Subscription, Transportation, and Travel.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<p>Still unsure or have more questions? </p><p>Please check our<a href=\"http://4retirees.com/support-centre/\" data-wplink-url-error=\"true\">Frequently Asked Questions</a></p>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2018-09-19 15:09:00','2018-09-19 05:39:00','',2,'http://4retirees.com/uncategorised/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(129,1,'2018-09-19 15:09:10','2018-09-19 05:39:10','<img src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Retirees4Retirees-nwagg2l083xsdvcvz2gw225hu8chkk7u6dp3xxhslc.png\" title=\"Retirees4Retirees\" alt=\"Retirees4Retirees\" />											\n		<p>We are 4Retirees, an online community where experience and opportunity meet.</p><p>We started with the belief that retirement is the career move we all wish we could make sooner. Its the fast track to freedom; A chance to take adventures off hold, rediscover your life, and start living those dreams.</p><p>After all, as a retiree, youve earned it. And we want to make sure you keep reaping the rewards. <br />Which is why we created 4Retireesan online community that shows you new ways to put your experience to work like sharing your skills online, meeting like-minded people, and profiting from the opportunities in the on-demand economy. <br />It may be a new way of doing things, but its perfect for people like us. Flexibility, freedom, and the income to live life on your terms; Its what we believe retirement is all about.</p><p><em><strong>4Retirees. Where wisdom meets fun.</strong></em></p>		\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"632\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Retirees4Retirees-Banner.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Retirees4Retirees-Banner.jpg 560w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Retirees4Retirees-Banner-133x150.jpg 133w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Retirees4Retirees-Banner-266x300.jpg 266w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n										<img width=\"179\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Vision.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Vision.png 179w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Vision-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 179px) 100vw, 179px\" />											\n		<h3>Our Vision</h3><p>4Retirees was created with one goal in mind; to help retirees take advantage of a new world of opportunities. We believe the online and on-demand economy offers a new way to future-proof your retirement dreams. It lets you earn additional income while still having the freedom to do the things you love most.</p><p>And it all starts with our online community, 4Retirees. Run for retirees and by retirees, you dont need tech-smarts. We let you learn from people just like you. No one knows better than a retiree how much the world changes. And 4Retirees is the network that helps you keep up. </p>		\n										<img width=\"179\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Mission.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Mission.png 179w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Mission-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 179px) 100vw, 179px\" />											\n		<h3>Our Mission</h3><p>We want 4Retirees to be a meeting place of ideas, inspiration, and experienced retirees. Together, we will create ongoing opportunities and an expanding network of support.</p><p>Our aim? To make us the number one resource for retirees. Whether youre looking to travel, to learn, or to follow a dream, well help you generate the income and knowledge you need. Because a lifetime of experience should always be rewarded.</p>		\n										<img width=\"179\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Promise.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Promise.png 179w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Icon-Our-Promise-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 179px) 100vw, 179px\" />											\n		<h3>Our Promise</h3><p>As a member of 4Retirees, youre part of a vibrant, welcoming community that helps generate all sorts of opportunities. Connect with like-minded retirees, discover and share new experiences, or enjoy the rewards of paid and voluntary workall online and off.</p><p>Along the way, youll collaborate with people just like yourself. People who are enthusiastic about making the most of their experience and their retirement. Together, we form the 4Retirees workforceone that is for retirees and by retirees. </p>		\n		<h3>4Retirees Manifesto</h3><p>Were for the most experienced generations. <br />For those whove shown us the way.<br />For the people who make us  us.<br />Retirees.<br />The people who smile on a Monday.<br />The people that experience has taught.<br />And those who know that retirement is lifes biggest reward. <br />Its why we are 4Retirees. <br />An online community that shares the same belief.<br />While life begins at retirement, we can make it even better.<br />We believe there are incredible opportunities. <br />To learn, to earn, and to see wisdom at work.<br />We believe in trading new skills and forging new friendships.<br />Amazing things can happen just by talking.<br />We believe technology is powerful too.<br />And retirement is the perfect time to put tech to work.<br />With the income it unlocks, retirees can carry on dreaming.<br />Adding new destinations and experiences to their list of to-dos<br />Because were all for rewards.<br />And for experience.<br />Were 4Retirees.</p><p><em><strong>Where wisdom meets fun</strong></em></p>		\n										<img width=\"687\" height=\"458\" src=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Our-Core-Values.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Our-Core-Values.jpg 687w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Our-Core-Values-150x100.jpg 150w, http://4retirees.com/wp-content/uploads/Our-Core-Values-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 687px) 100vw, 687px\" />											\n		<h3>Our Core Values</h3>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Empowering retirees\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Supporting your development \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Openness and authenticity\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Fostering inclusion \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Friendship and honesty\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Encouragement and independence\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Generosity \n									</li>\n								<li >