s at school or how their Little League team is going? Want to get back in touch with friends and relatives with whom youve lost touch or haven\'t seen in a long time?\r\n\r\nSocial networking sites such as <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/\">Twitter,</a> <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/\">Google+</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/\">Snapchat</a> are perfect for all of the above. They enable families, friends, and acquaintances to stay in regular contact with one another despite vast physical distances, and also enable people to meet and socialise with others both online and in real life.\r\n<blockquote>Get to know <a href=\"https://www.skype.com/\">Skype</a>, Facetime, <a href=\"https://www.messenger.com/\">Messenger</a>, <a href=\"https://allo.google.com/\">Allo</a> and <a href=\"https://duo.google.com/\">Duo</a></blockquote>\r\nAlso, videophone services such as <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\">Facebook,</a> <a href=\"http://www.skype.com\">Skype</a>, Facetime, <a href=\"https://allo.google.com/\">Goggle Allo</a> and <a href=\"https://duo.google.com/\">Google Duo</a> enable people to talk to friends and family face-to-face via their device almost anywhere. You can talk to your grandchildren in person about their day at school, hear how they are mastering the recorder for their upcoming concert, or how, Abis 5th birthday was last weekend. You can do all this even if you live on opposite sides of the world. With technology, you can now take a much more active role in the lives of your family and really embrace the role of being a parent or grandparent without ever having to fly anywhere.\r\n<h4>Technology Can Help You Be More Sociable</h4>\r\nMany recently retired people find themselves with a lot of time on their hands, as they no longer need to get up and go to work each day. Not having the social connections with your work colleagues might cause you to be lonely. You may well be looking for excuses to get out of the house, meet new people, and take up new pastimes.\r\n<blockquote>Looking to get out of the house, develop new interestsand meet new people?</blockquote>\r\nA simple Internet search can help you find clubs and community groups to help you do this. Also, the website <a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/\">MeetUp</a> enables people of all ages to create and join groups based on shared interests  be it movies, dining out, cycling, stamp collecting, football, religion, wine, gardening, etc.\r\n\r\nDid you know that you can also make new pen pals via the Internet? The website <a href=\"http://www.globalpenfriends.com/\">Global Pen Friends</a> is for people all over the world to become pen pals. Through this website, you can choose to be an e-mail pen pal, a postal pen pal, or both. Check regularly <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/4Retirees/\">4Retirees Facebook page</a> as we are creating local events for you to get involved and meet likeminded people.\r\n\r\nThese examples are just the tip of the Internet iceberg. Just know that modern technology can greatly encourage you to get out of the house and to meet people, and can greatly assist you in doing so.\r\n<h4>Technology Can Help You To Embrace Life and Learn More</h4>\r\nTheres more to life than just being social. And, technology can help you there too. Have you always wanted to learn Spanish? Or, trace your family tree? Want to try your hand at making a Peter Gilmore, MasterChef style snow egg? Maybe its time to embrace your inner-DaVinci but you need the right image for inspiration. Or do you feel the time is right for you to plan that round the world holiday and need to do some geo-research? Well, modern technology and Google tools, like <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/maps\">Google Maps</a>, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/\">YouTube</a>, and <a href=\"https://images.google.com.au/\">Google Image search</a> and many other google products that are free resource, teaching, and information sites are available at your fingertips. Once you master technology and focus it on your interests and dreams, youll wonder how you ever had time to work!\r\n\r\nTechnology can also greatly assist you right from your very own home, freeing up time that was wasted on the mundane while cutting out travel time. Thanks to modern technology, you can now do your shopping and your banking on-line without leaving the comfort of your own home, so you have more time for what you love and you can even shop in your pyjamas if you wish!\r\n<h4>Technology Can Increase Your Safety and Security</h4>\r\nYou can also use modern technology to increase your safety and security. For example, some retirement villages, apartments, and even individual homeowners are harnessing the latest in digital security camera equipment to increase the safety and security of residents. High-tech digital cameras not only deter the criminals they also give better picture quality than analogue ones, and subsequently make intruders easier to identify. Also, the fact that they are wireless makes them easier to position in the required locations, while enabling their signals to be fed to the monitoring stations. And if youre out most days, some monitoring tools can be viewed right from your smart phone giving you peace of mind knowing everything is secure at home.\r\n<h4>Technology Can Help You to Receive Medical Information and Treatment</h4>\r\nYou can also harness modern technology for medical purposes. You can find health related websites, healthy eating options, read the latest research and read information to help prevent things like arthritis and heart disease. You can ask Dr Google questions that you may have forgotten to ask your GP, or better yet, do your research first so you can have a more detailed and informed discussion with your healthcare practitioner.\r\n<blockquote>Dr Google can help but dont rely solely on the information you find.</blockquote>\r\nAnother example of how technology can help is the emergence of what is known as <a href=\"http://www.health.gov.au/internet/main/publishing.nsf/content/e-health-telehealth\">telehealth.</a> This is the practice of medical practitioners such as doctors and nurses harnessing modern communication technology, such as<a href=\"http://www.skype.com\"> Skype</a>, in order to communicate with patients and with each other. Doctors and patients no longer need to be in the same room together for a consultation to happen. Thus, if you live a long way from any medical clinics, you will no need to travel long distances for medical consultation, and doctors will no longer have to travel long distances to see you.\r\n\r\nThere are also what are known as health tracking technologies. These are very handy for seniors or anyone with a health condition like diabetes. Health tracking technologies such as apps and cloud-based record-keeping enable senior citizens and their caregivers to have regular access to the former\'s health information, such as medical conditions, medical contacts, medication schedules, etc.\r\n<h4>Technology Can Help you <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">Increase Your Income Opportunity</a></h4>\r\nIf it were not for technology, <a href=\"http://www.4Retirees.com\">4Retirees</a> wouldnt exist. We are an online community that brings together people with years of experience and the latest opportunities.\r\n\r\nWe will connect you to the power to unlock your maximum earning potential no matter what your age or situation! If you want to earn money in retirement, youre in the right place. <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com\">4Retirees</a> was created so you can access new ways to put your experience to work, like sharing your skills, both on and offline, while profiting from the opportunities in the on-demand economy.\r\n\r\nJoin us.\r\nTake the first step.\r\nComplete the <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">Free Income Compatibility Check</a> (with absolutely no further obligation)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Technology Can Help You Improve Your Fitness Level</h4>\r\nWhether you are tracking the number of steps you take each day through your <a href=\"https://www.fitbit.com/au/app\">Fitbit App</a> or booking a session with your physiotherapist through <a href=\"https://healthengine.com.au/\">HealthEngine</a> or easing into the day with your ow-impact exercise for mind and body using one of <a href=\"https://www.dailyyoga.com/#/\">Daily Yoga\'s</a> convenient workout plans, you will see how this technology enhanced world of apps for everything can add to your fitness in ways you never even imagined.\r\n\r\nAnd watch this space, for we take fitness seriously here at <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com\">4Retirees</a>. In fact, we will be posting new exercises daily as part of our getfit4retirees program. You will find links to these through our social media channels as well, so keep watch for great options, resources, tips and techniques so that you can become the fitness and most fabulous retired you possible.\r\n<h4>How 4Retirees Helps Unlock These Benefits and More</h4>\r\nSo, there you have it, these are just seven different areas where leveraging the power of contemporary technology can benefit you and help you to live the best retirement possible.\r\n<blockquote>You are not alone!</blockquote>\r\nYou might be thinking, This is all good news. But, I have trouble keeping up-to-date with all the modern technology. It goes over my head and I can\'t keep up.\r\n\r\nIf this is you, trust us when we say, You are not alone!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pewinternet.org/2014/04/03/older-adults-and-technology-use/\">In 2012, Pew Research conducted a poll of Americans aged 65 or over. Only 18 per cent of those polled felt comfortable using a new device such as a smartphone or tablet, while three quarters of them said they would need to be shown how to use them.</a>\r\n\r\nIn another study in 2014 Deakin University conducted a study that <a href=\"https://nationalseniors.com.au/be-informed/news-articles/genius-required-phone-plans\">found that mobile telephone contracts were too complicated for many people, so again, you are not alone. Theyre too complicated for most of us</a>.\r\n\r\nAround 2.7 million Australians aged 50 years and over have little or no engagement with the online world, according to <a href=\"https://nationalseniors.com.au/be-informed/news-articles/millions-older-australians-missing-out-online\">research from the Office of the eSafety Commissioner</a>, published in June of this year (2018).\r\n\r\nThe research also shows what you probably already know, that a major fear factor exists among older Australians who have low digital literacy, with technology often proving to be intimidating, reinforced by a lack of confidence to ask for help or knowledge of where to find it.\r\n<blockquote>THAT IS EXACTLY WHY <a href=\"http://www.4Retirees.com\">4RETIREES</a> IS HERE!</blockquote>\r\nWe are here for (4) you! We can help keep you informed daily so you too can get the most of technology from understanding your mobile contract, to which device is right for you, to finding all the great resources on the Internet. This is where <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">4Retirees</a> can be of great service.\r\n\r\nOur growing community provides regular information and tips on the modern technologies that retirees can tap into and shows you how to use them. We give you all the information you need, and in layperson\'s, terms so its simple to understand and delivered in a welcoming and supportive environment.\r\n<blockquote>Connect with other retirees via <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">4Retirees</a>\'</blockquote>\r\nRegularly visiting our website will make you a modern technology expert in no time. We bet that you will be showing your grandchildren what the latest in technology, rather than vice versa.\r\n\r\nAs a retiree, you can connect with other retirees via our 4Retirees\' <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/4Retirees/?ref=br_rs\">Facebook page</a>, where you can share what you have learnt and ask others for advice.\r\n\r\nAnd if you want to make some extra money to finance all these new retirement goals and dreams, you are in the right place!\r\n<blockquote>Well help you every step along the way</blockquote>\r\nSo, if you want to meet people, make connections, learn more about technology, enjoy your hobbies and interests, share your skills, work on your terms, or earn more than you thought possible?\r\n<h4>Want to get started now? Well help you every step along the way.</h4>\r\nThe earning opportunities available to you depend on your skills, interests and experience  <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">Complete Free Income Compatibility Check</a> and get your personalised list of opportunities one day, start making extra money the next!\r\n<h4>Get started!</h4>\r\nWhat kinds of jobs are out there? How do you find them? What skills do they need? How much can I earn? Join our growing community and well answer all these questions and more.\r\n\r\nRetirement is certainly changing. Welcome to the modern version of it. Your journey has only just begun and <a href=\"http://www.4retirees.com/\">4Retirees</a> will be there with you every step of the way to mentor you and ensure that you get access to the tools for making it the best retirement possible!','Modern Technology Delivers Mountains of Benefits for Retirees','','publish','open','open','','dolore-magna-aliquip-ut-incididunt-irure-pariatur-aute-adipisicing-9','','','2018-09-19 21:12:20','2018-09-19 11:42:20','',0,'http://4retirees.com/?p=145',0,'post','',0),(146,1,'2018-09-19 15:51:34','2018-09-19 06:21:34','Ut id labore adipisicing sed voluptate velit, qui in mollit, ipsum, duis quis. Sed ea tempor, fugiat voluptate aliqua, cillum exercitation duis magna ut excepteur mollit commodo, occaecat fugiat. Elit sed ullamco.\r\n\r\nDolore ut dolor, nostrud, est aliquip occaecat fugiat deserunt ipsu