5,'http://4retirees.com/uncategorised/145-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(155,1,'2018-09-19 16:18:18','2018-09-19 06:48:18','The benefits for retirees who stay abreast of modern technology are innumerable. If you want to have the best retirement life possible, you should embrace technology and get it working for you. It can help you:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Stay in touch with family and friends,</li>\n 	<li>Be more sociable,</li>\n 	<li>Embrace life and learn more,</li>\n 	<li>Increase home safety,</li>\n 	<li>Receive medical information and treatment.</li>\n 	<li><a href=\"4retirees.com\">Increase your opportunities to earn income</a></li>\n 	<li>Improve your fitness level</li>\n</ul>\nLet\'s say you have joined the burgeoning group of the recently retired. Youve got plenty of time to yourself, no work commitments, and are financially comfortable. Its time to take advantage of your newfound freedom. The world is your oyster. In fact, you might have already started doing all the things that youve always wanted but never had the time. Perhaps, youre a bit overwhelmed and might be wondering what to do with all this new-found freedom and spare time, thinking, \'What the heck do I do now?\'\n\nIn both these scenarios modern technology can be of great benefit and offer a variety of life-enhancing advantages.\n<h4>Technology Can Help You to Stay in Touch With Loved Ones</h4>\nDo you want to maintain contact with all your former work colleagues? Want to know how your grandchildren\'s day was at school or how their Little League team is going? Want to get back in touch with friends and relatives with whom youve lost touch or haven\'t seen in a long time?\n\nSocial networking sites such as <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/\">Twitter,</a> <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/\">Google+</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/\">Snapchat</a> are perfect for all of the above. They enable families, friends, and acquaintances to stay in regular contact with one another despite vast physical distances, and also enable people to meet and socialise with others both online and in real life.\n<blockquote>Get to know <a href=\"https://www.skype.com/\">Skype</a>, Facetime, <a href=\"https://www.messenger.com/\">Messenger</a>, <a href=\"https://allo.google.com/\">Allo</a> and <a href=\"https://duo.google.com/\">Duo</a></blockquote>\nAlso, videophone services such as <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\">Facebook,</a> <a href=\"http://www.skype.com\">Skype</a>, Facetime, <a href=\"https://allo.google.com/\">Goggle Allo</a> and <a href=\"https://duo.google.com/\">Google Duo</a> enable people to talk to friends and family face-to-face via their device almost anywhere. You can talk to your grandchildren in person about their day at school, hear how they are mastering the recorder for their upcoming concert, or how, Abis 5th birthday was last weekend. You can do all this even if you live on opposite sides of the world. With technology, you can now take a much more active role in the lives of your family and really embrace the role of being a parent or grandparent without ever having to fly anywhere.\n<h4>Technology Can Help You Be More Sociable</h4>\nMany recently retired people find themselves with a lot of time on their hands, as they no longer need to get up and go to work each day. Not having the social connections with your work colleagues might cause you to be lonely. You may well be looking for excuses to get out of the house, meet new people, and take up new pastimes.\n<blockquote>Looking to get out of the house, develop new interestsand meet new people?</blockquote>\nA simple Internet search can help you find clubs and community groups to help you do this. Also, the website <a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/\">MeetUp</a> enables people of all ages to create and join groups based on shared interests  be it movies, dining out, cycling, stamp collecting, football, religion, wine, gardening, etc.\n\nDid you know that you can also make new pen pals via the Internet? The website <a href=\"http://www.globalpenfriends.com/\">Global Pen Friends</a> is for people all over the world to become pen pals. Through this website, you can choose to be an e-mail pen pal, a postal pen pal, or both. Check regularly <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/4Retirees/\">4Retirees Facebook page</a> as we are creating local events for you to get involved and meet likeminded people.\n\nThese examples are just the tip of the Internet iceberg. Just know that modern technology can greatly encourage you to get out of the house and to meet people, and can greatly assist you in doing so.\n<h4>Technology Can Help You To Embrace Life and Learn More</h4>\nTheres more to life than just being social. And, technology can help you there too. Have you always wanted to learn Spanish? Or, trace your family tree? Want to try your hand at making a Peter Gilmore, MasterChef style snow egg? Maybe its time to embrace your inner-DaVinci but you need the right image for inspiration. Or do you feel the time is right for you to plan that round the world holiday and need to do some geo-research? Well, modern technology and Google tools, like <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/maps\">Google Maps</a>, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/\">YouTube</a>, and <a href=\"https://images.google.com.au/\">Google Image search</a> and many other google products that are free resource, teaching, and information sites are available at your fingertips. Once you master technology and focus it on your interests and dreams, youll wonder how you ever had time to work!\n\nTechnology can also greatly assist you right from your very own home, freeing up time that was wasted on the mundane while cutting out travel time. Thanks to modern technology, you can now do your shopping and your banking on-line without leaving the comfort of your own home, so you have more time for what you love and you c